\id 1CO  
\ide UTF8
\h 1 CORINTHIANS 
\toc1 Metamol Babior We Yael Paulus Ngalir Kristianol CORINTH 
\toc2 1 Corinthians 
\toc3 1 Co 
\mt1 CORINTH  
\is1 Hamadefal  
\ip \add Metamol babior we yael Paulus ngalir Kristianol\add* \bk Corinth\bk* ila ye teftaf bo yebe haposoloh weres kowe yesa holar yarmat irel kofael Kristiano mo tugulul ladep mo irel eklesia we Paulus ye chapidah mo woal Corinth. Irel yodla ngo Corinth ila sew haplomol Greece le ye palleng, ngo ila haplom la ye tamol le lamliyel Roma mo woal Achaia. Ye ffos idel haplom le irel mala kamdidiyal mo irel pallengel liliyel chuway iyang, mo yael yarmat ma toa faor maltemay ngo ye cholop rerel taliw iyang.  
\ip Mala ye kkel yael Paulus merah iyang ila yar harere yarmat mo yar Kristiano ma faor maltemay. Iwe mo irel meka kofal llepder mal mo fefel, mo kofal habulupoy, iwe mo hafelfelel halesiya mo kefang kala yael Espritu Santus mo molow tefael mo irel maes. Irel yael Paulus medaf mele yela yoh ngali le ye hamdefa sew kasiy ka mo irel Hapatpat Momay we.  
\ip Momol 13, we ye kapta kofael hachangcheng, le ila kefang la ye hartael kamdidiy mo luwul kefang ka yael Deus ngalir meka lol, ila sew momol le ye ffos idal mo lal babior le.  
\is1 Palpal Meka Yadol Babior Le  
\io1 Hamadefal \ior 1:1–9\ior*  
\io1 Yal harere Eklesia \ior 1:10—4:21\ior*  
\io1 Kaptal llepder mal mo fefel mo igegel yar be mel chol sew mo sew family \ior 5:1—7:40\ior*  
\io1 Rechoka re Kristiano mo rechoka rete Kristiano \ior 8:1—11:1\ior*  
\io1 Igegel yal mel Eklesia mo igegel mepel \ior 11:2—14:40\ior*  
\io1 Yael Kristus mo rechoka ye tugul lal deper molow tefael mo irel maes \ior 15:1–58\ior*  
\io1 Salpiy we re hateyili resa fang bo hammaler Kristiano kowe re mel woal Judea \ior 16:1–4\ior*  
\io1 Kofal iy llufulyal mo mala haygul loh \ior 16:5–24\ior*  
\c 1  
\s1 Metamol Babior We Yael Paulus Ngalir Kristianol  
\p
\v 1 Babior le ila ye budoh mo irel Paulus we Deus ye dipli bo yebe mel bo lol Kristus Jesus apostel, ngo ye wol budoh mo irel Sosthenes we bisich.   
\p
\v 2 Babior le ila ye loh ngalir yarmetael eklesia la yael Deus wol Corinth, mo panger rechokla resa ffesangur bo rebe mel bo lol Deus le rebe santus, le rechokla Deus sa lamlir bo resa sew chog mo Kristus Jesus. Iwe ngo resa wol sew chog mo panger yarmat lal faileng le, le rechokla rema hasrowu Samol la yach Jesus Kristus, le yar Samol ngo wol yach gich.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Ac 18:1\x*   
\p
\v 3 Deus le Temach mo Samol Jesus Kristus rebe fang ngalugmi haradiya mo hapos.   
\s1 Deus Ye Holbuwagich Irel Jesus Kristus  
\p
\v 4 Pangal yad ngo ima kangalu Deus la yai, yal hachigchig bo yaglugmi le fal haradiya la ye holahmi mo irel Jesus Kristus.  
\v 5 Bo hasa mmal irel pangal formel, mo pangal hapatpat, mo pangal repiy, le fael mala hasa sew chog mo Kristus.  
\v 6 Molwe kaptael Kristus we sa tugul long lal yami luluwal ila  
\v 7 tor sew yolbuw kala iyang le ye tohlahmi irel yodle ha wiwidi yodla Samol la yach Jesus Kristus yebe budoh iyang.  
\v 8 Yebe wol tipngugmi yebe kel chog dipmi yee, yela hola miril faileng, ralla bela tefaldoh Samol la yach Jesus Kristus ngo hasa mel le ha hartael momay ngo tor dermi.  
\v 9 Deus mele be tugul depach irel. Ila Deus la ye ffesangugmi bo habe sew chog mo Jesus Kristus le Lol ngo yach Samol.   
\s1 Eklesia Le Yesa Hamehal  
\p
\v 10 Fael mala idel Samol we yach Jesus Kristus ngo ibe hafal pechehmi pangmiloh rewol bisiy bo habe hasewa chog yami luluwal irel mekla hama sor, ila ngo ha towe rol hamehal. Habe mel le habe sew chog, ngo yebe sew chog yami luluwal mo mekla habe ma hatugulu.  
\v 11 Hami rewol bisiy, ye mel tot yarmat mo irel family we yael Chloe le re kangalu hamayiyey le hami hama rol hachocho fengal.  
\v 12 Mala ngang isosor ila mala semal hami ngo semat mele ye sor. Semal be sor bo, “Ngang choluwal Paulus”, ngo semal sa sor bo, “Ngang choluwal Apollos”, ngo semal sa sor bo, “Ngang choluwal Pedrus”; ngo semal sa sor bo, “Ngang choluwal Kristus.”\x - \xo 1:12 \xt Ac 18:24\x*  
\v 13 Ye hal sew holongol Kristus, le ila mele eklesia le towe yoh le sibe hamhela. Hare Paulus mele ye mes wol krud bo yaglugmi? Hare ha Baptismus bo habe mel bo re dabeyel Paulus?   
\p
\v 14 Ima kangalu Deus yal hachigchig le tor semal hami le ibaptismusgili bo halachog Crispus mo Gaius.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt Ac 18:8; Ac 19:29; Ro 16:23\x*  
\v 15 Ila tor semal le yebe sor bo hasa baptismus bo re dabeyey.  
\v 16 (Iwol baptismusgili Stephanas mo choal family la yal. Iwe ngo itay gola hare chil yor le iwol baptismusgili hare tayor.)\x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Co 16:15\x*  
\v 17 Kristus yete fangwey ngang iremi bo ibe baptismusgilugmi. Ye fang ngang bo ibe kangalugmi Hapatpat Momay we. Iwe ngo ibe kapta ngalugmi le itowe teptap meka repiyach yarmat bo yede torloh kelel yael Jesus Kristus la mes wol krud.   
\s1 Kristus Le Iy Mele Repiyal Mo Kelel Deus  
\p
\v 18 Bo kaptael kofael yal mes Kristus woal krud ila torloh pelal mo lal yar luluwal rechokla resa mwael loh. Iwe ngo ila mala kelel Deus mo irech gich ika siya daor.  
\v 19 Babior we ye santus ye sor bo,  
\q1 “Iy bele hachuyaloh repiy la yar rechokla re repiy,  
\q2 ngo iy bele hachuyaloh yar medaf rechokla sa tagiyet yar skun.”\x - \xo 1:19 \xt Is 29:14 (LXX)\x*   
\m
\v 20 Ila ngo meda mmaler rechokla ye palleng repiyer mo ikla ye palleng yar skun, hare rechokla re sallap irel hapalilil hapatpat? Deus ye kawraloh le mala repiyer yarmetael faileng le ila ye tor loh pelal.\x - \xo 1:20 \xt Job 12:17; Is 19:12; 33:18; Is 44:25\x*   
\p
\v 21 Bo irel mala repiyel Deus, ngo iy Deus yesa foru le towe yoh bo yarmat rebe gola iy Deus mo irel chog repiyer. Irel Hapatpat Momay le yarmat rema sor bo tor loh pelal mele Deus yesa hatugulu le yebe hadorar rechokla re chepar iyang.  
\v 22 Jews re faeg kemal bo yar tugul ngo Greeks re faeg repiy.  
\v 23 Iwe ngo gich ila si kekapta kofael Kristus we re krudu, le sew hapatpat le Jews rete dipli, ngo tor pelal mo lal yar Gentiles luluwal;  
\v 24 iwe ngo rechokla Deus yesa ffesangur, le Jews fengal mo Gentiles, ila hapatpat le mele Kristus, le iy mele repiyal mo kelel Deus.  
\v 25 Meka yarmat re sor bo ye buch Deus iyang, ila ye palleng repiy iyang mo imol meka repiyach yarmat; ngo meka yarmat re sor bo ye tayikel Deus iyang, ila ye kel mo imol meka kelach yarmat.   
\p
\v 26 Ha memangi chog rewol bisiy mokwe igegmi rallakowe irel yodwe Deus ye ffesangugmi iyang. Irel yach gich yarmat wiri ngo te cholop hami le ha repiy hare yor kelmi, hare ha tagiyet.  
\v 27 Deus ye spegil duwley mekla re faileng re sor bo tor pelal, bo fael mala yebe hamaalir rechokla re sor bo re repiy. Ye duwley mekla re faileng re sor bo tor kelal bo fael mala yebe hamaalir rechokla ye palleng keler.  
\v 28 Ye duwley mekla re faileng re tolpagili ngo rete dipli mo ikla re sor bo tor pelal, bo yebe hachuya loh mekla re faileng re sor bo ye palleng pelal.  
\v 29 Ila fal le tor semal le be yoh le yebe habos mo fael metal Deus.  
\v 30 Ngo ligdi bo Deus mele sa hasugmi bo habe rol sew chog mo Kristus Jesus, ngo Deus ye foru Kristus bo yebe mel bo repiyach. Kristus mele yesa hafelgich bo sibe fel mo irel Deus, ngo si mel bo lol Deus le si santus le iy mele sa hadoragich.  
\v 31 Ila molwe babior we ye santus ye sor bo, “Te tugul semal le ye dipli le be habos, ngo yebe habos irel mekla Samol yesa foru.”\x - \xo 1:31 \xt Jr 9:24\x*   
\c 2  
\s1 Kaptael Kristus We Re Kruduy  
\p
\v 1 Hami rewol bisiy, yodwe ibuyoy iremi ibe foloyu ngalugmi mekla ye katos we Deus ye itol we ye llebag, ngo ite foloy le iteptap hapatpat ka ye weres hare ifoloy le iwochog rechoka ye tagiyet yar skun.  
\v 2 Irel yodwe imel iremi ngo isa hatugulu mo lal yai luluwal le ibe mmaliglaloh pangal formel bo halachog Jesus Kristus we ye mes woal krud mele ibe itol chog lal yai luluwal.  
\v 3 Irel yodwe ibuyoy iremi ngo itayikel ngo irerer irel yai motog.\x - \xo 2:3 \xt Ac 18:9\x*  
\v 4 Ngo foloy ka yai mo meka ima kapta ila ite kapta mo irel meka repiyach yarmat, bo ikapta ngo ihatosiya irel mala kkelel Espritu Santus la Lamliyel Deus.  
\v 5 Yami tugul ila ye tamel irel repiyach yarmat bo ye mel irel mala kkelel Deus.   
\s1 Mala Repiyel Deus  
\p
\v 6 Ima foloyu kaptal repiy la yael Deus ngalir rechokla resa luglug ngal Kristus. Iwe ngo mele ila te repiyel yarmetael faileng le hare rechokla re tagiyet le yor kkeler lal faileng le. Rechokla ila ye tottorloh mala kkeler.  
\v 7 Repiy la ikekapta kofal ila repiy la yael Deus le ye llebag le yarmat re togla. Deus yesa faesul duwley mele mo imol yodwe be subdoh faileng le, bo yagel mala sibe falmay.  
\v 8 Tor semal rechokla ye tagiyet mo lal faileng le le ye gola iy repiy le. Bo hare re gola kofal, ila ngo towe yoh le rebe krudu Samol la ye falmay.  
\v 9 Iwe ngo babior we ye santus ye sor bo,  
\q1 “Meka ted yor mwo le ye wiri hare ye rongrong kaptal,  
\q2 mo mekla tor le ye luluwaleyloh le be wel,  
\q2 ila ikla mekla Deus yesa hafle bo fal ngalir rechokla re hachangi.”\x - \xo 2:9 \xt Is 64:4\x*   
\m
\v 10 Iwe ngo Deus yesa kkewar ngalgich mo irel Espritu Santus mekla iy ye yitol le ye llebag. Espritu Santus ye gola pangal formel, le ila mwo mekla Deus ye luluwaley le ye llebag.  
\v 11 Gich yarmat ila gich chog mele si gula meka ye mel lal luluwal ka yach. Ye hafedeg ngal chog yael Espritu Santus gola yael Deus luluwal.  
\v 12 Iwe ngo te mala repiyer yarmetael faileng le mele sa yoh ngalgich, bo Espritu Santus la Deus ye fangdoh mele yesa yoh ngalgich bo hare sibe gola pangal mekla Deus ye fang ngalgich.   
\p
\v 13 Gich ila si kapatpat le site tapeli hapatpat kala si gula mo irel meka repiyach yarmat, bo si tapeli mala si gula mo irel Espritu Santus irel yach hamdefa mala ye katos ngalir rechokla ye mel Espritu Santus uwor.  
\v 14 Semal le ye tamel Espritu Santus uwol ngo ye towe yoh ngali kkefang kala yema budoh mo irel Espritu Santus la lamliyel Deus. Tappel rechokla ila senger ila re temedaf irel meka. Ir re sor le tor pelal meka bo rechokla chog ye mel Espritu Santus uwor mele be yoh le rebe gola lepal momayel meka.  
\v 15 Te tugul semal le ye mel Espritu Santus uwol ngo be yoh la be gola momayel pangal formel, ngo tor semal le yebe yoh le yebe hatugulu kofal.  
\v 16 Babior we ye santus ye sor bo,  
\q1 “Itey le ye gola yael Samol luluwal?  
\q2 Itey le be yoh le yebe foloyu Samol?”  
\m Iwe ngo gich ila yesa yoh ngalgich luluwal we yael Kristus.\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Is 40:13 (LXX)\x*   
\c 3  
\s1 Re Hagloy Kala Yael Deus  
\p
\v 1 Hami rewol bisiy, towe yoh le ibe hapatpat ngalugmi le yebe wochog yai hapatpat ngalir rechokla ye mel Espritu Santus uwor; ye tugul le ibe hapatpat ngalugmi le yebe wochog yai hapatpat ngalir yarmetael faileng le. Hami ila ha chil wochog yalwich irel lepal yami medaf irel tugulul ladep le yar Kristiano.  
\v 2 Irel yodwe ngo milik mele iholugmi bo ha ted fel le habe mongoy. Igla mwo ngo ha ted fel,\x - \xo 3:2 \xt Hb 5:12–13\x*  
\v 3 bo ha chil mel le hami yarmetael faileng le. Yodla habe rol loltomay fengal, ngo ha rol hachocho fengal, ila ngo yete ikla mekla ye hallehaloh le hami yarmatael faileng le ngo hasa dabey wegdeg kala yar?  
\v 4 Yodla semal hami yebe sor bo, “Ngang choluwal Paulus”, ngo semal be sor bo, “Ngang choluwal Apollos”, — ila ngo hated dabey mekla wegdigir rechokla re togla Deus?\x - \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Co 1:12\x*   
\p
\v 5 Itey le Apollos? Ngo itey le Paulus? Hamem chog yael Deus re hagloy le ha pepalugmi bo habe chepar. Semal gich ngo ye foru yengang kala Samol ye fang ngali bo yebe foru.  
\v 6 Ngang mele ifadgu faesol ire we ngo Apollos mele yema yidfi ngal chael, iwe ngo Deus mele ye foru bo yebe tumul fedah we.\x - \xo 3:6 \xt Ac 18:4–11; Ac 18:24–28\x*  
\v 7 Yeramtala yema fedagu mo yeramtala yema yidfi fedah we ila tor pelar. Deus mele yor pelal bo iy mele ye foru bo yebe tumul fedah we.  
\v 8 Tor mele ye dil mo llepdal yeramtala yema fod mo yeramtala yema yidfi fedah we. Deus yebe fang paliyer le be dabey lepal mekla semal mo semal ir ye foru.  
\v 9 Bo hamem chog chol sew yengang le ha yengang ngal Deus, ngo hami mele milay la yael Deus.  
\p Ngo wol hami imw la imwel Deus.  
\v 10 Iteptap kkefang la yael Deus le ye fang ngalyey, iwe isa foru yengang kala yar salap irel yai feta sew dayif. Iwe ngo semal yesa budoh fatlah uwol. Iwe ngo semal ngo yebe kemahoy hamayu igegel yal fatlah.  
\v 11 Sa mol yael Deus yitol le Jesus Kristus mele dayif, ngo tayor sew dayif le yebe chil ffaor mo solbos.  
\v 12 Tot yarmat re bele teptap hoal hare silver hare feas ka ye changcheng bo rebe hassu wol dayif la; ngo tot ila rebe teptap ire hare fadil.  
\v 13 Momayel yael semal mo semal yengang ila be llah irel Ralla be tefaeldoh Kristus iyang. Irel Ralla ngo yaef ye bele hagla ngo ye kawraloh mala halongol igegel yael semal mo semal yengang.  
\v 14 Hare te fisngeg mala semal ye fatleha mo wol dayif la, ila ngo be yor paliyel yal yengang.  
\v 15 Iwe ngo hare ye fisngegloh mala semal ye fatleha ila ngo towe yor paliyel yengang la yal. Ngo iy llufulyal ila yebe daor le be wochog molwe ye cheway mo luwul yaef.   
\p
\v 16 Ye tugul bo ha gola le hami ila yael Deus templum ngo Espritu Santus ila ye mel uwomi!\x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Co 6:19; 2 Co 6:16\x*  
\v 17 Ila semal le be hatawsi templum la yael Deus ngo Deus yebe lliyloh. Bo templum la yael Deus ila ye santus ngo hami mele yal templum.   
\p
\v 18 Tor semal le ma iy chog yal kacchepra. Hare yor semal mo luwullumi le ye luluwaley ngo ye gola pangal meka repiyer re faileng le, ngo yebe yitli le tor mele iy ye gola, ila ngo yebe yoh ngali repiy.  
\v 19 Bo mala yarmetael faileng le re yitli bo ila mala repiy, ila tor loh pelal mo irel Deus. Babior we ye santus ye sor bo, “Deus ye dorfir rechokla re sor bo re repiy luwul yar machohchoh”;\x - \xo 3:19 \xt Job 5:13\x*  
\v 20 ngo babior we ye santus ye wol sor bo, “Samol ye gola le luluwal kala yar rechokla re repiy ila tor pelal.”\x - \xo 3:20 \xt Ps 94:11\x*  
\v 21 Ila tor semal le yebe habos irel meka ma yoh le yarmat rebe foru: Mala halongol igegal ila pangal formel ngo yami,  
\v 22 le Paulus mo Apollos mo Pedrus mo faileng le mo molow mo maes mo igla mo wagey. Pangalloh meka ngo yami,  
\v 23 iwe ngo hami ila Kristus mele ye lamlugmi iwe ngo Deus mele ye lamli Kristus.   
\c 4  
\s1 Apostel Kowe Lol Kristus  
\p
\v 1 Habe luwaley le hamem yael Kristus re hagloy le resa yitlugmem bo habe kapta mekla ye katos ngo ye llebag le lamliyel Deus.  
\v 2 Mala ye tugul le re hagloy la yebe foru ila yebe yitol depal irel yal yengang ngal masta la yal.  
\v 3 Ngang ite luluwaleloh mekla hami ha hatugulu hare mekla yarmat re hatugulu bo kofay. Ngang mwo ngo itema hatugulu kofay.  
\v 4 Tor mele ye tafel mo lal yai luluwal, ngo ligdi bo te ila mele yebe hatugulu le tor mele itayikof iyang. Samol mele yebe hatugulu mele ngang ibe mel iyang.  
\v 5 Ila ha towe hatugulu mele semal yebe mel iyang mo imol mala be hola yodla iy. Mala hartael hatugul ila yebe widi yodla yebe budoh Samol iyang. Yebe hallehaloh luluwal kala yar yarmat le ye llebag. Iwe ngo Deus bele fang ngal semal mo semal lepal hapingping la ye tugul bo yebe yoh ngali.   
\p
\v 6 Fael hami rewol bisiy mele isa tapeli meka ngalugmem mo Apollos bo hare hamem habe mel bo sew hammedaf ngalugmi bo hami habe gola fael mele re sor bo, “Ha taelenga hatobtob ka ye fel.” Tor semal hami le yebe cchehas irel semal yarmat ngo ye tolpagililoh ila semal.  
\v 7 Itey le ye forugmi bo habe tagiyet mo imor ikla sibis? Te Deus mele ye fang ngalugmi pangal formel? Ila ngo be ifa sengal chog ngo ha sala habos le hare yebe wochog molwe te kkefang mekla ye yoh ngalugmi?   
\p
\v 8 Pangal mekla habe mmal iyang ngo yesa yoh ngalugmi! Hami igla ila hasa mmal! Hasa rol mel bo king le ila mwo hamem ha ted king? Iyalyal bo hare tos le hami hasa rol mel bo king bo hare be yoh le pangachloh ngo sibe rol mel bo king.  
\v 9 Iluluwaley ngo Deus sa yitlugmem apostel le hamem mele habe hamirloh. Habe wochog rechokla resa hatugulu le rebe mes mo fael meter yarmat cholop le panger angelus mo yarmetael faileng le ngo rebe wurugmem.  
\v 10 Hamem hasa yitili le tor mele ha gola le fael Kristus, ngo ligdi bo hami hasa mel le hasa repiy irel yami sa sew chog mo Kristus. Hamem ila ha tayikel ngo hami ila ha kkel. Hamem ila tor pelamem ngo hami ila ha ssor.  
\v 11 Sa hola doh igla ngo hamem hama betbat ngo ha mesel kolohloh chog. Ngo hama mengag irel pisil mengag. Rema llugmem ngo hama tofotngag fedal chog;  
\v 12 iwe ngo hasa peyagus irel kkelel yamem yengang. Yodka rebe mapelahmem bo habe hafohoy ngo hamem hama mapelar bo rebe yolbuw. Yodka rebe hafohoyugmem ngo hama yedamgel irel mekla rema faor ngalugmem.\x - \xo 4:12 \xt Ac 18:3\x*  
\v 13 Yodla rebe hapatpat tayikof ngalugmem, ngo hamem hama hatefaeli ngal hapatpat kala ye momay. Hamem ila hasa hafedeg ngal meka pisir re faileng le. Hamem ila tordoh chog pelamem lal faileng le yee, yela hola doh igla.   
\p
\v 14 Isa tefa babior le ngalugmi le te mil mala ibe foru bo habe maa, bo fael mala ibe foloyugmi le be wochog mala hami spegil layi.  
\v 15 Ila mwo ifa lepal yarmat le re kekefalugmi irel yodle hasa mel bo Kristiano iyang ngo halachog ila ye hal semal chog tammi le ye mel. Irel yami mel le hasa sew chog mo Kristus Jesus, ngo isa mel le ngang tammi bo fael mala ngang mele ihasidoh Hapatpat Momay we iremi.  
\v 16 Ila ibe hafael pechehmi bo habe ma somla meka ima foru.\x - \xo 4:16 \xt 1 Co 11:1; Phil 3:17\x*  
\v 17 Ila fal le isa hagloyuwey Timothy iremi, bo iy ila yesa mel le spegil layi fael Kristiano ngo ihachangi. Iy mele be hamangiya ngalugmi foloy kala ye tefoy le ima dabey irel yamem sa sew chog mo Kristus Jesus. Ika maka ima foloyu ngalir pangal eklesia pangal lobos.   
\p
\v 18 Tot hami ila hasa cchehas bo hasa kacchog le itowol buyoy tefael mo iremi.  
\v 19 Hare be fel mo irel Samol, ila ngo towol ssulay ngo ibele buyoy tefael mo iremi. Iwe ngo ibele moch la spegil wiri lepal kkeler rechokla re habos bo hare ye ppalu ngali mekla ir re kapta.  
\v 20 Bo mala Lamliyel Deus ila te hapatpat chog bo yor kkelal.  
\v 21 Ifa sew le ha dipli? Ibe buyoy le ibe hasiwey sew woawo, hare ibe buyoy luwul maluluy mo hachangcheng?   
\c 5  
\s1 Kkelel Tayikof Irel Eklesia  
\p
\v 1 Igla ila yarmat re sor bo sa mel sew wegdeg tayikof luwulumi le rechokla mwo rete Kristiano ngo towe yoh le rebe foru. Yarmat re kangaluyey bo ye mel semal mal mo luwulumi le yema hamsuru semal fefel le ril mala temal!\x - \xo 5:1 \xt Dt 22:30\x* \f + \fr 5:1 \ft Fefel la ila te spegil sil mal le.\f*  
\v 2 Ila ngo be ifa sengal chog ngo hasa habos? Susul mala yebe tayikof dipmi irel mele ngo mal la ye for mele iye sengal ila ye momay le yebe chuy bo towol mel bo chilami.  
\v 3-4 Ila mwo iddaw tangugmi ngo luluwal le yai ila ye mel iremi, ngo fael mala idel Samol la yach Jesus, ngo sa mol yai hatugulu kofael mal la ye foru wegdeg le ye tayikof. Ha bela ttey fengal ngo ngang ibe mel iremi irel mala kkamelal Samol la yach Jesus le ye mel irech.  
\v 5 Ila habe ngaley Satan mal le bo yebe lliyloh mala holongol bo hare yebe yoh le yebe daor mala ngul irel Ralla yebe budoh Samol iyang.   
\p
\v 6 Ye tafel le hami habe habos! Hami ngo ha gola molwe rema sor bo, “Sugfed chog habboloh ngo ye palleng flowa la yebe boloh iyang.”\x - \xo 5:6 \xt Ga 5:9\x*  
\v 7 Habe hachuya habboloh la sa ssulay le ila mele molfid bo habe taldag. Ila ngo ha bele wochog sew flowa le ye tefoy le tor habboloh iyang, ngo igula le ila sangmi. Bo Gublul Paska we rol yach ila sa fel igla le resa fang Kristus we iy mele Saaf we maligach irel Paska.\x - \xo 5:7 \xt Ex 12:5\x*  
\v 8 Si towe gubulu Paska le yach irel flowa we yor habboloh we sa ssulay iyang, bo habboloh la mele wegdeg kala ye tayikof mo molfid. Sibe gubulu irel flowa la tor habboloh iyang bo flowa le mele taldag mo katos.\x - \xo 5:8 \xt Ex 13:7; Dt 16:3\x*   
\p
\v 9 Irel babior we itefawey iremi ngo ikangalugmi bo ha towe choluwa ngalir rechokla rema for maltemay.  
\v 10 Mele ila ite sor le rechokla rete Kristiano le rema faor maltemay, hare rechokla re chehaw, hare re machoh, hare rechokla rema mepel ngal todeb. Habe rel chuy mo lal faileng le, ngo sa moch yoh la habe haddaw tangir tappel rechoka.  
\v 11 Mala ngang ikekapta ila ha towe choluwa ngal semal le ye sor bo ibismi ngo yema faor maltemay hare ye chehaw hare ma mepel ngal todeb hare yema hatayikofa kaptal yarmat hare ye ma habbelasloh chog hare iy semal cho machoh. Ha towe mongoy ngalir taper rechoka iye senger.   
\p
\v 12-13 Te ngang mele ibe hatugulu kofer rechokla te ir Kristiano. Deus mele yebe hatugulu kofer. Te sul mo sengal le hami mele habe hatugulu kofer mekla choluwami? Babior we ye santus ye sor bo, “Ha hachuya yeramtala ye tayikof wegdegel mo luwullumi.”\x - \xo 5:12-13 \xt Dt 13:5; 17:7 (LXX)\x*   
\c 6  
\s1 Kristiano Re Hasiloh Mekla Choluwar Lal Court  
\p
\v 1 Hare semal hami ye hapaliyel ngal semal choluwami Kristiano, ngo meda fal le be loh irel chol tatelal hapatpat kala te ir Kristiano ngo yete ligdi bo mekla lol Deus rebe taldi mala re song fengal iyang?  
\v 2 Ha togla le mekla lol Deus mele rebe hatugulu kofer re faileng? Iwe ngo hare hami mele habe hatugulu kofer re faileng, ila ngo towe yoh ngalugmi le habe taldi tot lofidfid le ye ppachigchig?  
\v 3 Ha togla le gich mele sibe hatugulu kofer angelus? Ila ngo meda weresel le gich sibe hatugulu kofal ika ye mel irel molow le si mel iyang?  
\v 4 Hare bela weldoh sew formel le iye sengal, ngo habe hasiloh irer rechokla tor igegar mo irel eklesia le yach bo rebe hatugulu kofal?  
\v 5 Hate maa? Ye tugul le yor mo luwulumi le re repiy le be yoh ngalir le rebe taldi fedgel hapatpat kala llepdami Kristiano.  
\v 6 Iwe ngo hami ha chil ma loh court ha bela yichingewa semal bismi Kristiano. Iwe ngo rechokwe rete chepar mele re bele hatugulu kofal molwe.   
\p
\v 7 Mala hama hasiloh semal court ila ye kawraloh le teyoh ngalugmi meka wegdegel Kristiano. Yete far momay le yarmat rebe for ngalugmi mekla ye tayikof. Yete far momay le rebe hasi tangugmi mekla litami.  
\v 8 Far hami chog yami hatayikofa fengalugmi ngo ha pere fengali petegel semal mo semal hami. Kristiano kala chilami mwo ngo hama faor ngalir meka!  
\v 9 Ye tugul bo ha gola le rechokla ye tayikof wegdeger ila towe yoh ngalir mala Lamliyel Deus. Towe hami chog yami kacheprahmi; Tapper rechoka rema faor maltemay hare rema mepel ngal todeb hare rema paoy sew mo rechoka te yar habulupoy, hare mal ka rema for maltemay ngalir mal, hare fefel ka rema for maltemay ngalir fefel,  
\v 10 hare rechoka rema peraf, hare rechoka re chehaw, hare retoa habbelas, hare rechoka rema hatayikofa kapter sibis, hare rechoka re machoh, ila tor semal ir le yebe hola mala Lamliyel Deus.  
\v 11 Yor tot hami le ila senger metamo. Iwe ngo igla ila hasa taldag mo irel molfid, ngo hasa mel bo lol Deus. Hasa fel mo irel Deus irel mala kkelel Samol Jesus Kristus mo Espritu Santus.   
\s1 Habe Tapeli Mekla Holongomi Irel Falmay La Yael Deus  
\p
\v 12 Semal be sor bo, “Te tugul mele iy ngo be yoh le ibe foru.” Tos le ila sengal, ngo te pangal formel ngo ye momay ngalugmi. Ngang be yoh le ibe sor bo te tugul sew formel ngo be yoh le ibe foru, ngo itowe faor sew formel bo yebe yusuwiliyeyloh.\x - \xo 6:12 \xt 1 Co 10:23\x*  
\v 13 Semal yebe wol sor bo, “Pelal mele mongoy ila yadol siyel yarmat, ngo pelal siyel yarmat ila liliyel mongoy.” Roruwow meka ngo yor siyal mo irel Deus. Ila ha towe tapeli holongomi irel wegdegel maltemay. Habe tapeli irel yami yengang ngal Deus. Bo Deus mele yema fang hammalel holong.  
\v 14 Deus ye hamolowa tefaeli Samol mo irel maes. Ngo yebe wol tapeli mala kkelal bo yebe hamolowa tefaeligich mo irel maes.   
\p
\v 15 Hami ngo ha gola le mekla holongomi ila chilal mala holongol Kristus. Ifa sengal, be yoh le ibe kak mo irel mekla chilal mala holongol Kristus bo ibe hachungali holongol semal fefel le yema tap chuway holongol? Ye tugul bo towe yoh!  
\v 16 Medalbo ha ted gola le semal mal le yebe fang mala holongol ngal semal fefel le yema tap iy chuway ngo resa sew chog holong? Ye ffod yael babior we ye santus sor bo, “Ir rorumal ngo re bele mel le resa sew chog holong.”\x - \xo 6:16 \xt Gn 2:24\x*  
\v 17 Iwe ngo semal le yebe fang iy ngal Samol, ila rebe sew chog mo Samol.   
\p
\v 18 Ha towe foru wegdegel maltemay. Molfid kala tot le semal yebe foru ila tor mele be faor ngal holongol. Ngo semal le be for maltemay ila yesa foru sew molfid le ye tayikof ngal holongol.  
\v 19 Ha togla le mekla holongomi ila yael Espritu Santus templum, le ye mel iremi ngo Deus mele ye fang ngalugmi? Te hami chog yami lamlugmi bo Deus mele ye lamlugmi.\x - \xo 6:19 \xt 1 Co 3:16; 2 Co 6:16\x*  
\v 20 Yesa mol yal chuwayugmi le ye cchaw palimi le ye fang. Ila ha tapeli mekla holongomi ngal falmay la yael Deus.   
\c 7  
\s1 Kasiyel Kofael Habulupoy  
\p
\v 1 Igla ila ibele kapta kofael kasiy we yami we ha tefalong lal babior we ha fangdoh irey. Ha sor bo ye momay le mal re towe riri.  
\v 2 Iwe ngo mil mala yesa kkel wegdegel maltemay mele ye momay le be panger mal ngo be yor yar habulupoy, ngo panger fefel ngo be wol yor yar habulupoy.  
\v 3 Semal mal ngo ye fang holongol ngal yal habulupoy, ngo be wol ila sengal semal fefel ngal mal la yal habulupoy. Bo be semal ir ngo ye hafel depel ila semal.  
\v 4 Bo semal fefel le ye habulupoy ila te iy mele ye lamli mala holongol, bo mal la yal habulupoy mele ye lamli. Wol ila sengal semal mal le ye habulupoy, bo te iy mele ye lamli mala holongol, bo habulupoy la yal mele ye lamli.  
\v 5 Towe mmal le habe temechal masor sew mo yami habulupoy; yodla be mmal le ha towe masor sew iyang, ila sew yad le hami hasa hatugulu fengali bo habe tapeli bo habe mepel. Iwe ngo bela wol miril ngo hasa wol ma masor sew mo habulupoy kala yami, bo dela yoh le Satan ye wigdi dipmi le fael mala tay yoh le habe holu tefaeli mekla dipmi.   
\p
\v 6 Ikangalugmi mele le ite dding ngalugmi bo habe foru; yai kangalugmi chog mele le sew formel le ye tal ngalugmi le habe foru.  
\v 7 Ihable le hare pangamiloh ngo ha wochog ngang. Ngo halachog ila semal ngo ye musloh kkefang la Deus ye fang ngali, ye fang ngal semal semat kkefang, ngo ye fang ngal ila semal semat kkefang.   
\p
\v 8 Iwe ngo hami mal kala tor yami habulupoy, mo hami fefel kala sa mes yami habulupoy, ila ye far momay ngalugmi le ha bele taboloh yami paoy chog llufulumi, la be wochog ngang.  
\v 9 Ngo hare towe yoh ngalugmi le habe hamachulong mekla luwalel lal dipmi, ila ngo ha sala habulupoy — bo ye momay le habe habulupoy mo imol mala ha bela hamachulong chog luwalel lal mekla dipmi.   
\p
\v 10 Iwe ngo hami rechokla hasa habulupoy, ila ye mel sew hatobtob le te yai bo yael Samol le ye sor bo: tor semal fefel le be ligdi yal habulupoy.\x - \xo 7:10 \xt 7:10–11; Mt 5:32; 19:9; Mk 10:11–12; Lk 16:18\x*  
\v 11 Iwe ngo hare semal fefel yebe ligdi yal habulupoy, ila ngo be paoy chog llufulyal le towe habulupoy hare ye tefael bo rebe hafle fengali llepder mo habulupoy we yal. Iwe ngo tor semal mal la yebe hachuya yal habulupoy.   
\p
\v 12 Iwe ngo ngang (spegil ngang le, te Samol) ibe kangalugmi ikla sibis bo: Hare semal mal le ye Kristiano yesa paoy ngali semal fefel le yete Kristiano, ngo fefel la ye dipli le rebe taboloh yar popaoy sew iwe ngo mal la ye towe hachuya fefel la.  
\v 13 Iwe ngo hare semal fefel le ye Kristiano yesa paoy ngal semal mal le yete Kristiano, ngo hare iy mal le ye dipli chog le rebe taboloh yar popaoy sew mo fefel la, ila ngo fefel la ye towe ligdi mal la.  
\v 14 Bo mal la yete Kristiano ila yesa fel mo irel Deus le fael fefel we ye Kristiano we yal habulupoy we resa sew chog; iwe ngo fefel la yete Kristiano ila yesa fel mo irel Deus le fael mwal we ye Kristiano we yael habulupoy we resa sew chog. Bo hare be te iye sengal, ila ngo mekla layur ila rebe haffedeg ngalir layur rechokla rete Kristiano. Iwe ngo wululul yar mel igla ila re fel mo irel Deus.  
\v 15 Hare yeramtala yete Kristiano yesa dipli le yebe ligdi habulupoy we yal we ye Kristiano, ila ngo hasa ligdi bo ila. Iwe ngo irel tapel mele iye sengal, ngo yeramtawe ye Kristiano ila ye tal mo irel habulupoy we yal, te tugul hare iy semal mal hare iy semal fefel. Deus ye ffesangugmi bo habe mel luwul hopos.  
\v 16 Be ifa sengal ngo gel semal fefel le ho Kristiano ho sala gola hare be yoh ngalug le hobe hadora mal la yam habulupoy? Ngo be ifa sengal ngo gel semal mal le ho Kristiano ho sala gola hare be yoh ngalug la hobe hadora fefel la yam habulupoy?   
\s1 Ha Dabey Fofos La Yael Deus  
\p
\v 17 Semal ngo ye mel le yebe dabey igegel kkefang la Deus yesa fang ngali, bo ila mele Deus yesa fang ngali. Iye mele ngang ifofoloyu ngal pangal eklesia.  
\v 18 Hare semal le sa faesul hagil yesa talenga fofos la yael Deus, ila ngo iy yetowe luluwaley le yebe hachuya hagil la mo uwol. Iwe ngo hare semal mal le yeted hagil yesa talenga fofos la yael Deus, ila ngo iy yetowe hagil.  
\v 19 Te tugul hare semal mal ye hagil hare yete hagil, ngo tor pelal. Mala ye palleng pelal, ila mala semal yebe talenga hatobtob kala yael Deus.  
\v 20 Semal ngo yebe mel chog irel mala faesul igegal irel yodla Deus ye ffesangu iyang.  
\v 21 Gel semal slave irel yodwe Deus ye ffesangug iyang? Hachuyaloh mo lal yam luluwal. Iwe ngo hare yebe mmal ngalug le hobe foru bo hobe tal, ila ngo hosa foru.  
\v 22 Bo semal slave le Samol yesa ffesangu, ila yesa mel bo lol Samol ngo yesa tal. Iwe ngo semal le ye tal le Kristus yesa ffesangu, ila yesa mel bo lol Kristus re hagloy.  
\v 23 Deus yesa chuwayugmi le ye cchow palimi; ila ha towe mel bo layur yarmat slave.  
\v 24 Rewol bisiy, pangami ngo habe mel chog irel Deus le be igegel chog yodwe Deus ye ffesangugmi iyang.   
\s1 Rechoka Tor Rir Mo Fefel Ka Sa Mes Rir  
\p
\v 25 Iwe ngo irel kofael kasiy we ha kasiydoh irey irel kofer rechoka rete habulupoy: ila tor mele Samol ye kangaluyey iyang. Iwe ngo ibe sor mala yaladepey iyang. Luwul ffahol ladep la yael Samol, ngo ngang yor igegay le habe luglug irey.   
\p
\v 26 Irel kofael weres le igla ila, ye far momay le semal mal ngo ye mel chog irel wululul mala iy ye faesul mel iyang.  
\v 27 Yor semal fefel le yam habulupoy? Ila ngo ho towe luluwaley hobe hachuya. Ho ted habulupoy? Ila ngo ho towe ffag yam habulupoy.  
\v 28 Iwe ngo hare ho habulupoy, ngo hote molfid iyang. Iwe ngo hare semal fefel le ye ted habulupoy yesa habulupoy, ngo iy yete molfid. Idipli le ibe teladugmi mo irel weres kala ma holar cho habulupoy seral mo seral.   
\p
\v 29 Iye fael meka isosor rewol bisiy: tay lap time le ye meldiy igla, ngo bele chaep igla sa loh le mal ka re habulupoy ila rebe mel la rebe wochog molwe rete habulupoy;  
\v 30 Iwe ngo rechoka re tetang ila rebe forurloh le medalbo tetayikof lal deper; iwe ngo rechoka re memmal ila rebele forurloh le medalbo te cchehas lal deper. Iwe ngo rechoka re chuchuway formel, ila rebele forurloh le medalbo te pitgir mokwe resa chuwayi;  
\v 31 iwe ngo rechoka re yengang bo yebe cholop liter, ila re bele forurloh le medalbo te ikla mele ye kkel yar luluwaley. Bo mele igegel faileng le igla ila, towol ssulay yal mel le be iye sengal.   
\p
\v 32 Idipli le habe tal mo irel yami merahrahloh chog. Semal mal le yete habulupoy ila, yebe itol chog depal irel yengang kala yael Samol, bo iy ye yeyedamgel bo yebe hafel depel Samol.  
\v 33 Iwe ngo semal mal le yesa habulupoy ila, ye itol chog depal irel meka kofal talop le, bo fal mala ye dipli le yebe hafle depel habulupoy la yal;  
\v 34 ila mal la, ila sa ruwow yal luluwal mo iyang. Iwe ngo semal fefel le tor yal habulupoy, hare semal le ted golar mal, ila ye itol chog depal irel yengang kala yael Samol bo ye dipli le yebe fang ngol mo holongol ngal Samol; iwe ngo semal fefel le yesa habulupoy ila yema itol chog depal irel meka kofael talople le fael mala ye dipli le yebe hafel depel habulupoy la yal.   
\p
\v 35 Isosor mele le fael mala idipli le ibe tupungugmi. Ite luluwaley le ibe hawersugmi. Ifar dipli le hami habe foru mekla ye fel ngo ye momay, ngo habe fang holongmi mo yami luluwal irel yengang kala yael Samol, le tor mele habe hammach tefaeli.   
\p
\v 36 Be iye sengal kofer rechoka re kapta fengaliy bo rebe paoy sew ngo yela wol miril ngo resa sor bo re towol paoy sew. Hare mal la ye luluwaley ngo ye tafel wegdegel ngal fefel we, ngo hare ye kkel yael dipli fefel we ngo ye dipli le rebe habulupoy, ila ngo ye momay le rebe habulupoy bo ila mala iy ye dipli. Ngo tor molfidil mele.  
\v 37 Iwe ngo hare semal mal le iy chog llufulyal yal hatugulu le towe riri, iwe ngo yesa kkel depal le iye mele yebe foru, ngo yesa faesul tugul yal luluwal irel mala iy yebe foru, ila ngo ye momay le yetowe riri.  
\v 38 Ila mal la ye habulupoy ila ye fel mala ye foru, iwe ngo ila yete riri ila ye wol kkel tot yal fel ila ye foru.   
\p
\v 39 Semal fefel le ye habulupoy ila yete tal irel yodla ye molow mal we yal habulupoy iyang; iwe ngo bela mes habulupoy la yal, ngo iy bele moch tal le yebe rili semal mal le iy ye dipli, igle mal la ila iy semal Kristiano.  
\v 40 Fefel la ila yebe kkel tot yal rraey igle ye mel chog le towe riri. Iye mele yaladepey. Iwe ngo ngang iluluwaley ngo Espritu Santus la lamliyel Deus ila ye mel irey.   
\c 8  
\s1 Kasiyel Kofael Mongoy Kala Rema Tape Maligach Ngal Liyosol Todeb  
\p
\v 1 Ibele kapta kofal mokwe ha tefa irel kofael mongoy ka yarmat rema tap maligach ngal liyosel todeb.  
\p Ye katos bo “pangachloh ngo siya medaf” le ila sengal we hami ha sor, ngo ligdi bo tappel mala ila yema hakkela yar yarmat hattodah. Iwe ngo hachangcheng ila yema fang kkelach.  
\v 2 Semal le ye luluwaley le sa palleng golayel irel sew formel ila ted kkeral le be gola lepal mala be yoh le be gola.  
\v 3 Iwe ngo yeramtala ye hachang Deus ila Deus ye gola.   
\p
\v 4 Kofal mongoy kala sima hangi le sima tap maligach ngal liyosel todeb: si gula le todeb kala ila te katos; pangach ngo si gula le halsemal chog Deus.  
\v 5 Ila mwo yor mekla re sor bo “deus,” le hare ye mel wol laeng hare wol talop, ngo tos le ye cholop meka re sor bo “deus” hare “samol,”  
\v 6 iwe ngo gich ila ye halsemal chog Deus le Temach, ngo iy mele ye Hasub pangal formel ngo gich si molow le fael iy. Ngo halsemal chog Samol Jesus Kristus, le ye sub pangal formel mo irel ngo gich si molow le fael iy.   
\p
\v 7 Yete pangal yarmat ngo re gola le iye mele ye katos. Tot yarmat resa yaoru yar ma mepel ngal liyosel todeb le la ralleka, ngo rebe mongoy tappel mongoy ka rema tap maligach, ngo rema luluwaley chog le mongoy ka ila hal todeb. Ye tayikel yar luluwal ngo rema sor le mongoy we yebe hatayikkofar.  
\v 8 Ngo ligdi bo mongoy we ila ye towe haflegich mo irel Deus. Tor mele yebe budoh mo iyang le hare site mongoy, iwe ngo wol tor mele yebe budoh mo iyang le hare si mongoy.   
\p
\v 9 Habe hafalliy bo yami wegdeg yede forur rechokla ye tayikel yar tugul rebe ppunglong luwul molfid.  
\v 10 Hare wochog bo semal le ye tayikel yal luluwal irel kofael mele, yedela wurugmi rechokla rema sor bo ha “repiy,” le ha momongoy lal templum la yael semal todeb; ila ngo ye towe far hakkela depal le yebe mongoy mongokala rema fang ngal todeb?  
\v 11 Iwe ngo yeramtawe ye tayikel depal le yesa mel bo bismi we ye mes Kristus bo fael iy, ila yebele mes le fael “mekla golayemi”!  
\v 12 Be iye sengal ngo hasa molfid ngal Kristus bo fael mala hasa molfid ngalir Kristiano kala bismi bo hasa hatayikofa luluwal kala yar le ye tayikel.  
\v 13 Hare mongoy mele sa wigdi depel mala bisiy ngal molfid, ila ngo tayor fael sew le ibe chil mongoy fodog bo fael mala yede weg depel mala bisiy ngal molfid.   
\c 9  
\s1 Kkelal Mo Yael Semal Apostel Yengang  
\p
\v 1 Te ngang semal yarmat le italdag? Hare te ngang semal apostel? Hare ited wiri mwo Jesus le yach Samol? Hare te ngang mele itupngugmi bo habe mel bo yael Samol chol yengang?  
\v 2 Ila mwo tot yarmat rete yitilyey le ngang semal apostel ngo hami ha gola le ngang semal apostel. Fael mala hasa sew chog mo Samol mele hami hasa mel bo tugulul mala ngang semal apostel.   
\p
\v 3 Yodka yarmat rebe hapatpat tayikof irey ngo iye mele ima foru:  
\v 4 Ye tafel le ibe mongoy ngo iyul chael formel bo payel yai yengang?  
\v 5 Hare apostel kowe sibis mo Pedrus mo mokwe bisil Samol rema hasi mokwe rir irel yar malekah, ila ngo ngang tor igegay le ibe wol foru?  
\v 6 Hare hamem chog mo Barnabas mele habe yengang bo yebe yoh ngalugmem salpiy?  
\v 7 Yor semal saldaw le ma iy chog yal ffag paliyel hammalel? Hare yor semal chol milay le te ma yul uwal milayel \add grape\add* la yal? Hare yor semal chol matmetal saaf le te ma kak milk mo irel saaf kala lol?   
\p
\v 8 Te kofal chog meka sima foru seral mo seral mele ibe kangalugmi, bo tappel chog meka molwe Hatobtob we ye wol sor.  
\v 9 Ye teftaf irel Hatobtob we yael Moses le ye sor bo, “Ha towe fargu yewal semal karbow irel yodla ye susuru \add grain\add* kowe bo yebe mustang mokwe sewal.” Iwe, karbow mele Deus ye luluwaley kofal?\x - \xo 9:9 \xt Dt 25:4; 1 Ti 5:18\x*  
\v 10 Te gich mele Deus ye kekapta kofach irel molwe ye sor meka? Ye tugul le molwe ye teftaf ila fal ngalgich. Yeramtala yema kkamchogchogu boll sew milay mo yeramtala yema gilsi uwal milay we, ila re yengang ngo re luluwaley le yebe yor yildir mo irel uwal milay we.  
\v 11 Hasa fang ngalugmi fedah la ye momay le ila mele yalol Deus. Ila ngo yebe kkel yal weres ngalugmi le hare habe fang sugfed bo hammalmem?\x - \xo 9:11 \xt Ro 15:27\x*  
\v 12 Hare yor pelar sibis yarmat le habe foru ngalir mele, ila ngo hamem te palleng tot pelamem le habe wol faor ngalugmem?  
\p Hamem hate luluwaley le habe kak chog hammalmem mo iremi. Hama yedamgel irel pangal formel bo dela temmal folol Hapatpat Momay le kofael Kristus.  
\v 13 Ye tugul le hami ngo ha gola le rechokla rema yengang ila yor haler le ma buyoy mo lal Templum we. Iwe ngo rechokla rema fang maligach wol altar ila ma yor yildir mo irel maligach kowe.\x - \xo 9:13 \xt Dt 18:1\x*  
\v 14 Wol ila sengal molwe Samol ye sor, le rechokla rema foloyu Hapatpat Momay we ila be yor hammaler mo irel mala re foforu.\x - \xo 9:14 \xt Mt 10:10; Lk 10:7\x*   
\p
\v 15 Iwe ngo ngang ited tapeli mwo iy hammal ka. Iwe ngo ite tefa babior le lea hare mil mala ibe sor bo ibe kak hammaley mo iremi. Ye momay le ibe mes mo imol mala ibe faor mele! Tor semal le yebe sor bo ye kachepar meka isosor.  
\v 16 Tor mmaley le ibe habos irel mala ima foloyu Hapatpat Momay we. Ila mala re kangaluyey bo ibe foru. Yebe kkel yai hafohoy le hare ibe te foloyu Hapatpat Momay we!  
\v 17 Hare ngang chog lufulyey mele iluluwaley ibe foru yengang le, ila ngo ibe luluwaley bo be yor paliyey. Iforu mele bo yagel mala ila mele yai yengang le Deus ye fang ngalyey.  
\v 18 Meda mele paliyey le ma yoh ngalyey? Mala paliyey ila mala ngang ima foloyu Hapatpat Momay we, ngo itema sor bo yebe yor paliyal. Iwe ngo itowe sor bo yor kkaley irel yai foloyu Hapatpat Momay le.   
\p
\v 19 Ngang semal yarmat le italdag, bo tor le ngang lol slave, ngo ligdi bo isa foru bo ibe mel bo yar panger yarmat slave, bo hare be cholop yarmat le rebe weg ngal Kristiano.  
\v 20 Ibe mel luwullur Jews le ibe fofoloyu Hapatpat Momay we, ngo ima mel le iwochog semal Jews bo hare ir rebe weg ngal Kristiano. Ila mwo tor pelal Hatobtob we yael Moses ngalyey, ngo ima mel le ye wochog molwe ima dabey Hatobtob le bo mil mala rebe weg.  
\v 21 Wol ila chog sengal yodka ima mel luwullur Gentiles le ifofoloyu Hapatpat Momay we, bo ima mel le iwochog semal ir le ite dabey hatobtob kowe yar Jews, bo yagel mala rebe weg ngal Kristus. Mele ila te mil mala hare ite dabey Hatobtob la yael Deus. Ngang ila idabey Hatobtob la yael Kristus.  
\v 22 Ibela mel luwullur rechoka tayikel yar tugul irel Kristus, ngo imel le iwochog semal ir bo hare rebe weg ngal Kristus. Pangal mekla be yoh le ibe faor ngalir yarmat, ngo ima foru bo hare be yoh le ibe hadora tot ir.   
\p
\v 23 Ima foru pangal meka le fael Hapatpat Momay we bo yebe yoh ngalyey pangal yolbuw kala yema budoh mo iyang.  
\v 24 Ye tugul le ha gola le ma cholop chol hagrumel ddar. Iwe ngo halsemal mo luwullur mele yema yoh ngali mala paliyal. Hala dabey hagrum bo be yoh ngalugmi mala paliyal.  
\v 25 Panger chol kokom ka ngo rema dabey chog hatobtobol kokom kala re kekay bo fael mala be yoh ngalir marmar kala tema ssulay. Iwe ngo gich sibe faor mele bo yebe yoh ngalgich marmar la tor siyal.  
\v 26 Ila fal le iddar le iwwel ngal lobosla yarmat re hagrum ngali. Ila fal le iwochog semal chol tug kowe yete ma hatolpa yal tug.  
\v 27 Isa hafaetagi mele holongoy le ye wochog yael semal chol tug hafaetagi holongol. Isa foru mele bo ibe lamli mele holongoy, bo dela wol miril yai foloyur panger yarmat ngo Deus ye hachuyayey mo irel hagrum le.   
\c 10  
\s1 Kristiano Re Towe Ma Mepel Ngal Todeb  
\p
\v 1 Hami rewol bisiy, idipli bo habe memangiy chog molwe ye wel ngalir chapdoh kowe yach we re dabey Moses. Panger ngo madpil darmiy we mele ye tipingir iwe resa darsupiloh Red Sea le tor mele re foru.\x - \xo 10:1 \xt Ex 13:21–22; Ex 14:22–29\x*  
\v 2 Irel darmiy we mo tad we mele la panger ngo re baptismus bo choluwal Moses iyang.  
\v 3 Panger ngo re mongoy flowa we ye budoh mo irel Deus\x - \xo 10:3 \xt Ex 16:35\x*  
\v 4 ngo re yul chael we Deus ye fang mo irel hogyal we ye dedaber. Hogyal le ila Kristus.\x - \xo 10:4 \xt Ex 17:6; Nu 20:11\x*  
\v 5 Ngo ligdi bo te pangerloh ngo ye fel depel Deus ngalir, ila fal le re mes ngo ye medar fedal mekla porgor lal tolmayloh we.\x - \xo 10:5 \xt Nu 14:29–30\x*   
\p
\v 6 Igla ila pangal meka ngo sa mel le sew hammedaf ngalgich, le yebe hadpa ngalgich bo si dela foru tayikof kowe ir re foru.\x - \xo 10:6 \xt Nu 11:4\x*  
\v 7 Si towe mepel ngalir todeb le be wochog molwe sibis ir re foru. Babior we ye santus ye sor bo, “Yarmat resa marodiy bo rebe gubul ngo re habbelas ngo re foru maltemay.”\x - \xo 10:7 \xt Ex 32:6\x*  
\v 8 Si towe foru wegdegel maltemay kowe sibis ir re foru, iwe lal seral chog ngo riyeg mo suluw sangeras ir le re mes.\x - \xo 10:8 \xt Nu 25:1–18\x*  
\v 9 Si towe hagla Samol le be wochog molwe tot ir re foru iwe parchoyoh sala llimeserloh.\x - \xo 10:9 \xt Nu 21:5–6\x*  
\v 10 Si towe hapaliyel ngal Deus le be wochog molwe tot ir re foru iwe molwe Angelusel Maes sala llimeserloh.\x - \xo 10:10 \xt Nu 16:41–49\x*   
\p
\v 11 Pangal meka ngo ye wel ngalir bo sew hammedaf ngalir yarmat, iwe ngo ye teftaf lal babior bo yebe hadpagich, bo siya mel irel sew yad le sa harep ngal miril faileng.   
\p
\v 12 Semal le ye luluwaley ngo sa fel igegal, ngo ye momay le yebe llugu depal bo yede ppunglong luwul molfid.  
\v 13 Pangal hagelgel kala sa holahmi ngo yema faesul holar yarmat. Iwe ngo Deus ila yema foru meka yesa hatugulu. Iwe ngo ye towe mechal bo rebe haglahmi le be ligdiloh lepal mala be yoh ngalugmi; bo yodla rebe haglahmi iyang, ngo iy yebe fang kkelmi bo be yoh ngalugmi hagelgel la, ngo ye fang yalapmi bo habe tal mo iyang.   
\p
\v 14 Ila hami rewol maryarey, ha towe ma mepel ngal todeb.  
\v 15 Ikapatpat ngalugmi le hami sibis yarmat le ha repiy; ha luluwaley kofael meka ngang isosor.  
\v 16 Kap we si teptap irel mongol fehaf we yael Samol ngo sima kangalu Deus yal hachigchig iyang, ila yodla sibe yul mo iyang, ngo siya sew chog irel mala cchal Kristus. Iwe ngo flowa we si dipiy ila yodla sibe hangiy, ngo siya sew chog irel mala holongol Kristus.\x - \xo 10:16 \xt Mt 26:26–28; Mk 14:22–24; Lk 22:19–20\x*  
\v 17 Bo fael mala halsew flowa mele pangachloh, le ila mwo si cholop, ngo siya sew chog bo mil mala si mongoy chog mo irel sew flowa.   
\p
\v 18 Ha luluwaler yarmetael Israel kowe. Rechokwe rema mongoy mokwe resa tap maligach, ila resa rol sew chog irel maligach we resa fang ngal Deus wol altar.\x - \xo 10:18 \xt Lv 7:6\x*  
\v 19 Meda fal iy mele ngang isosor kofal? Isosor bo hare yor pelal todeb kala hare mongoy kala rema tap maligach ngali?  
\v 20 Yeb! Mele ngang isosor ila mekla rema tap maligach wol altar kala yar rechoka rete Kristiano ila re fang ngal moniyan, ngo rete fang ngal Deus. Iwe ngo ite dipli le hami habe dabey moniyan.\x - \xo 10:20 \xt Dt 32:17 (LXX)\x*  
\v 21 Towe yoh le habe yul mo irel kap la yael Samol, ngo ha wol yul mo irel kap la yar moniyan; iwe ngo towe yoh le habe mongoy mo irel tis la yael Samol, ngo ha wol mongoy mo irel ila yar moniyan.  
\v 22 Hare si dipli le sibe foru bo yebe ngol Samol? Hare si chicchiy le si kkel mo imol?\x - \xo 10:22 \xt Dt 32:21\x*   
\p
\v 23 Rema sor bo, “Ye tal ngalgich le sibe foru mele si dipli.” Tos iy mele ngo halachog ila te pangal formel ngo ye momay. “Sa tal ngalgich le sibe foru mele si dipli” — ngo te pangal formel ngo ye momay ngalgich.\x - \xo 10:23 \xt 1 Co 6:12\x*  
\v 24 Towe semal ngo ye meri chog mekla iy ye dipli, bo yebe wol luluwaley mmaler yarmat.   
\p
\v 25 Ha tal le habe mongoy pangal fodog kala rema tap chuway mo loboka rema tap chuway fodog mo iyang, ngo tor mele ye tafel mo irel mala habe mongoy fodog ka.  
\v 26 Bo iwe babior we ye santus ye sor bo, “Talop mo pangal mekla ye mel iyang ngo lamliyel Samol.”\x - \xo 10:26 \xt Ps 24:1\x*   
\p
\v 27 Hare semal rechokwe ye ted Kristiano ye fesangugloh irel imwal ha bela mongoy, iwe ngo hami hasa dabey bo habe loh, ha mongoy mekla rebe fang halmi. Ha towe kasiy kofal bele tor mele ye tafel mo iyang.  
\v 28 Iwe ngo hare semal sa kangalugmi bo, “Mongoy le ila re tap maligach ngal todeb,” ila ngo hami ha towe hangi mongoy la bo yagel yeramtawe ye kangalugmi molwe bo yede tafel yal luluwal.  
\v 29 Mele ila te yami luluwal, bo yael ila semal luluwal mele habe hafle.  
\p Iwe ngo semal yesa kasiy bo, “Ila ngo meda fal le ital ngo ibela ppoloh bo fael mala de tafel yael semal luluwal?  
\v 30 Hare ikangalu Deus yal hachigchig irel mongoy ka helay, ila ngo meda mele semal yebe lunguyey iyang le hare ikangalu Deus yal hachigchig?”   
\p
\v 31 Te tugul mele ha foru, hare ha mongoy hare ha yul, ngo habe foru bo fael falmay la yael Deus.  
\v 32 Habe mel le ha towe tayikof ngalir Jews hare Gentiles hare eklesia le yael Deus.  
\v 33 Ha foru meka ngang ima foru; Ima yedamgili chog bo ibe hafle deper panger yarmat irel pangal meka ima foru. Ite ma luluwaley chog mmaley llufulyey, bo ima luwalley mmaler panger yarmat, bo hare ir rebe daor.   
\c 11  
\p
\v 1 Ha somlayey le yebe wochog yai somla Kristus.\x - \xo 11:1 \xt 1 Co 4:16; Phil 3:17\x*   
\s1 Ha Totawo Chimi Irel Yodla Habe Mepel  
\p
\v 2 Ibe hapingpingahmi bo fael mala pangal yad ngo ha luluwaleyey ngo ha dabey foloy ka ikangalugmi.  
\v 3 Ngo idipli le habe gola bo Kristus mele ye lamlir panger mal, ngo mal ila re lamlir fefel kala yar habulupoy. Iwe ngo Deus mele ye lamli Kristus.  
\v 4 Semal mal le ye mepel, hare ye kapta mala yalol Deus luwullur yarmat ngo ye totawo chemal ila yete hasrowu Kristus.  
\v 5 Ngo semal fefel le ye mepel hare ye kapta mala yalol Deus luwullur Kristiano le tor mele ye totawo ngal mala chemal, ila yete hasrowu mal la ril. Iwe ngo tor mele ye dil mo lepder mo semal fefel le ye gurchaliloh chemal.  
\v 6 Hare semal fefel yete totawo chemal, ngo ye momay le be guruloh mala chemal. Ngo ye hamama le semal fefel yebe guruloh chemal. Ila ye momay le yebe totawo chemwal.  
\v 7 Tor pelal le semal mal yebe totawo chemal bo fael mala ye mel mala igegal mo momayel Deus uwol. Ngo fefel ila ye mel mala momayel mal we uwol;\x - \xo 11:7 \xt Gn 1:26–27\x*  
\v 8 bo mal ila rete budoh mo irer fefel, bo fefel mele re budoh mo irer mal.\x - \xo 11:8 \xt 11:8–9; Gn 2:18–23\x*  
\v 9 Ngo rete sub mal bo yaglir fefel, bo fefel mele re sub bo yaglir mal.  
\v 10 Bo fael ir angelus mele ye momay la fefel rebe totawo chemar, bo yebe kawraloh le mal kowe rir mele re lamlir.  
\v 11 Irel molow le yach irel Samol ngo fefel ila ye tafel le rebe mel le be ir loh chog, iwe ngo wol ila chog senger mal.  
\v 12 Bo fefel ila re budoh mo irer mal: iwe ngo mal ila re sub mo irer fefel. Iwe ngo Deus mele ye faor pangal formel.   
\p
\v 13 Ha luluwaley ngo ye fel la semal fefel yebe mepel ngal Deus le yebe te totawo chemal?  
\v 14 Hasa faesul gola le ye hamaama mele mal rema halelayi chemer.  
\v 15 Ngo mala ila sew hamohmoh mo irer fefel. Meka yalchemer fefel le yema lellay ila ye mel le totol chemer.  
\v 16 Hare semal yebe hapaliyel ngalyey irel mele, ngo mala chog ibe sor ila, gich mwo yarmetal eklesia ka yael Deus, ngo tayor kkoch mo solbos le sibe dabey irel yodla sibe mepel ngal Deus iyang.   
\s1 Mongol Fehaf We Yael Samol  
\r (Matthew 26:26–29; Mark 14:22–25; Luke 22:14–20)  
\p
\v 17 Meka ibele moch kapta ila ite hapingpingahmi iyang, bo fael mala habe ttey fengal ngo ye cholop tayikof mo imol ikla ye momay le yema budoh mo iyang.  
\v 18 Metamol ngo re kangaluyey bo hasa rol harere irel yami ttey, ngo mele ila ichepar le yor tot mo iyang le ye katos.  
\v 19 (Ye tugul le hama rol harere bo yagel mala yebe llahloh rechokla ir mele re bung.)  
\v 20 Te Mongol Fehaf we yael Samol mele hami hama hangi irel yodkala hama ttey fengal iyang.  
\v 21 Bo habe la rol ttey fengal bo habe rol mongoy, ngo sa semal hami ngo ye hangi chog hal llufulyal, iwe sala meldiy sibis hami le re mesel kkolog ngo sibis ikla resa belas.  
\v 22 Tor bugtami le habe mongoy ngo ha yul mo iyang? Hare ha dipli habe hattolop ngal eklesia la yael Deus ngo ha hamaalir rechokla re hafohoy? Meda mele hami ha luluwaley le ngang ibe sor irel kofal mele? Ibe hapingpingahmi? Ye tugul bo ituwe foru!   
\p
\v 23 Bo meka ngang mele ifoloyu ngalugmi ila ye yoh ngalyey mo irel Samol: llubngul rallawe re fangloh Samol Jesus, ngo ye hasi sedep flowa,  
\v 24 sa kangalu Deus yal hachigchig, ngo sa dipiy flowa we ngo sa sor bo, “Mele ila holongoy le sa mel bo yaglugmi. Ha foru mele bo iy be ma mmang ngalugmi.”  
\v 25 Wol ila sengal chog mele ye foru mo wol miril yar mongol fehaf. Ye hasi kap we ngo sa sor bo, “Kap le ila bugtag we ye tefoy we yael Deus, le mele cchay mele tugulul. Te tugul sew yad le habe yul mo iyang, ngo habe foru bo iy be ma mmang ngalugmi.”\x - \xo 11:25 \xt Ex 24:8; Jr 31:31–34; Ex 24:6–8\x*   
\p
\v 26 Pangal yad le habe hangi flowa le ngo ha yul mo irel kap le, ngo hama kapta yal mes Samol Jesus yee, yela hola yodla be tefaeldoh iyang.  
\v 27 Ila fal le te tugul semal le be hangi flowa le ngo ye yul mo irel kap le yael Samol, ngo tor pelal mo lal yal luluwal ngo yesa molfid bo sa tolpagili mala holongol mo cchal Samol.  
\v 28 Ila fal le semal ngo ye luluwaley hamayi mwo kofal llufulyal, ngo sa moch hangi flowa le ngo ye yul mo irel kap le.  
\v 29 Bo hare yete luluwaley fael molwe holongol Samol irel yodwe ye hangi flowa we ngo ye yul mo irel kap we, ngo sa iy chog yal ffag yal hagerger irel yodla ye mongoy ngo ye yul mo iyang.  
\v 30 Ila fal le ye cholop hami le resa tomay ngo re tayikel, ngo tot hami ila resa mes.  
\v 31 Hare metamol chog ngo siya luwaley hamayi kofach, ila ngo towe hola gich hagerger la yael Deus.  
\v 32 Samol yesa hatugulu kofach ngo ye fang yach hagerger bo fal mala si towe chungalir yarmetal faileng le irel hagerger kala yar.   
\p
\v 33 Iwe ngo hami rewol bisiy ila, yodla habe ttey fengal le habe hangi Mongol Fehaf we yael Samol, ngo hasa widi semal mo semal hami.  
\v 34 Ngo hare semal hami yesa kkoloh sala mongoy mo llubugtal. Ila ngo towe holagmi hagerger la yael Deus irel yodla habe ttey iyang. Chil mel tot le ibe rel buyoy ngo si moch hafle kofal.   
\c 12  
\s1 Kkefang Kala Ye Budoh Mo Irel Espritu Santus  
\p
\v 1 Ibele kapta kofal mokwe ha teftafdoh babior irey iyang, we ha kasiydoh kofal kkefang kala ma budoh mo irel Espritu Santus.  
\p Idipli le hami rewol bisiy habe gola mala tosal.  
\v 2 Hami ha gola le yodwe ha ted Kristiano, ngo ye cholop loboskla ha dalib mo iyang, ha sala memapel ngal todeb.  
\v 3 Idipli bo habe gola le tor semal rechokla ye mel Espritu Santus uwol le be yoh le be ssupah hal Jesus! Iwe ngo yebe tamel Espritu Santus uwol semal ngo towe yoh le be sor bo, “Jesus ila iy Samol”.   
\p
\v 4 Ye cholop metmetael kkefang, iwe ngo semal chog Espritu Santus mele yema fang.\x - \xo 12:4 \xt 12:4–11; Ro 12:6–8\x*  
\v 5 Ye cholop metmetael hassor, iwe ngo semal chog Samol le sima hasrowu.  
\v 6 Ye cholop metmetael sallap, iwe ngo semal chog Deus mele yema fang salaper yarmat bo fael yengang kala yar.  
\v 7 Ye llah Espritu Santus mo uwol semal mo semal, bo yagel mala be tipingir panger yarmat.  
\v 8 Espritu Santus yema fang kkelel kasemal yarmat bo yebe repiy yar foloy, ngo Espritu Santus la chog mele yema wol fang kkelel kasemal bo yebe hammedaf yar foloy.  
\v 9 Espritu Santus la chog mele yema fang tugulul ladep ngal kasemal, ngo ye fang kkelel kasemal bo rebe ma hachuya yar yarmat tomay.  
\v 10 Espritu Santus la chog mele yema fang kkelel kasemal bo rebe ma ffaor kkemal, iwe ngo wol iy chog mele yema fang kkelel kasemal be yoh la rebe ma kapta mekla yalol Deus. Ngo yema wol fang kkelel kasemal bo rebe gola kkefang kala ye budoh mo irel, mo ikla te budoh mo irel. Ngo yema fang kkelel kasemal bo be yoh le rebe hapatpat irel semat hapatpat le ye wwel ngo ye wol fang kkelel kasemal bo be yoh le rebe hamdefa.  
\v 11 Iwe ngo iy chog Espritu Santus mele ye foru pangal meka. Iy mele ye dipli be fang kkefang, le semal ngo semat kkefang la yebe fang ngali.   
\s1 Halsew Holong Ngo Ye Cholop Wocchol  
\p
\v 12 Kristus ila ye wochog sew holong le ye cholop wocchol; Heramwo rete hafedeg fengal mekla wocchol, ngo re chil mel chog le sew holong.\x - \xo 12:12 \xt Ro 12:4–5\x*  
\v 13 Ila be wol ila sengach chog pangachloh le te tugul hare Jews hare Gentiles, slave hare te slave, iwe ngo semal chog Espritu Santus le ye baptismus yagilgich bo sibe sew chog. Iwe ngo Deus yesa fang ngalgich Espritu Santus bo yebe mel lal bulach.   
\p
\v 14 Bo sew holong ila te sew loh chog bo ye cholop wocchol.  
\v 15 Hare sere pechech yebe sor bo, “Te ngang chilal holong le bo te ngang sere paol yarmat,” iwe ngo towe yoh le yebe mustang holong we.  
\v 16 Ngo hare sere talengach ye sor bo, “Ngang ila te chilal holong le bo te ngang sefaes metal yarmat,” iwe ngo towe yoh le yebe mustang holong we.  
\v 17 Hare holong we ila sew chog faesul metal yarmat, ngo be ifa sengal ngo sa rongrong formel? Ngo hare be sere chog talengel yarmat, ngo be ifa sengal ngo sa rongrong bol formel?  
\v 18 Iwe ngo iye sengal igegel holong la Deus ye foru. Deus ye foru sew mo sew meka madpil holong le le be wochog mala iy ye dipli.  
\v 19 Towe yoh le be halsedep ngo sala mel bo sew holong.  
\v 20 Mala igegal igla, ila ye cholop madpil ngo hal sew holong.   
\p
\v 21 Ila towe yoh le sefaes metach be kangalu paoch bo, “Itowe teptap gel!” Hare chemach ye kangalu pechech bo, “Itowe teptap gel!”  
\v 22 Towe far ila sengal. Towe yoh le sibe sor bo tor pelal solbos mo uwoch le hare ye tayikel;  
\v 23 iwe ngo lobos kala si luluwaley le te palleng hames pelal mo uwoch ila, ila lobos kala sima far hafalmangi fedaley chog; iwe ngo lobos kala ye tafel le yarmat rebe wiri mo uwoch ila sima lebagili,  
\v 24 iwe ngo site ma foru mele ngal lobos kala ye momay mo uwoch. Deus mele ye foru holong le bo be ila sengal, bo fael mala be ssor tot lobos kala gich si luluwaley le tor pelal mo uwoch.  
\v 25 Holong le ila sew chog ngo towe yoh le be mehalhal, ngo pangal lobos mo wol holong le ngo rema tipingi fengalir.  
\v 26 Hare be hafohoy solbos mo wol holong we, ngo pangal lobos mo wol holong we ngo rebe dabey irel hafohoy; ngo hare rebe hapingpinga solbos mo wol holong we, ila ngo pangal lobos mo wol holong we ngo rebe dabey irel rraey.   
\p
\v 27 Pangmiloh ngo hasa mel bo holongol Kristus, le semal hami ngo ye mel bo solbos mo wol mala holong.  
\v 28 Deus yesa hatugulu ragregel yarmat mo lal eklesia. Metamol ngo apostel, ngo harwowal ngo sa profeta, yela hasuluwal ngo sa chol foloy, iwe ngo sa rechokla rema ffaor kkemal, iwe ngo sa rechokla yor kkeler le rebe hachuya yar yarmat tomay hare re tipingir yarmat, hare re haddarlahor yarmat, hare rechokla rema hapatpat irel semat hapatpat le ye wel.\x - \xo 12:28 \xt Eph 4:11\x*  
\v 29 Te pangal yarmat ngo apostel, hare profeta hare chol foloy. Te pangal yarmat ngo yor kkeler la rebe ffaor kkemal,  
\v 30 hare rema hachuya yar yarmat tomay, hare rema hapatpat irel semat hapatpat le ye wel, hare rema hamdefa iy hapatpat kala ye wel.  
\v 31 Ha yedamgili kkefang kala ye palleng fal.  
\p Ngo ligdi bo mala ye hartael momay ila iye ibele moch kangalugmi.   
\c 13  
\s1 Hachangcheng  
\p
\v 1 Haramwo yela yoh le ibe hapatpat irel yalol sew mo sew fulu hare yalol angelus, iwe ngo hare tor depel hachangcheng irey, ila ngo meka ikapta ila tor loh pelal le ye wochog kkungul parang kowe rema hakkunguloh chog le tor loh pelal.  
\v 2 Hare isallap irel foloy ngo yesa yoh ngalyey pangal repiy ngo igula pangal mekla ye llebag, ngo ye kkel yai tugulul ladep la be yoh le ibe hamgudu sew tayit mo liliyal, iwe ngo hare be tor depel hachangcheng irey, ila ngo ngang ila tor loh pelay.\x - \xo 13:2 \xt Mt 17:20; 21:21; Mk 11:23\x*  
\v 3 Haramwo ifangloh pangal meka litay, ngo ila mwo ifang mele holongoy bo rebe fisgi, iwe ngo hare tor depel hachangcheng irey, ila ngo tor mele ibe mmalli mo iyang.   
\p
\v 4 Hachangcheng ila malulu mo momayel hagiyeg; hachangcheng ila te loltomay hare habos;  
\v 5 hachangcheng ila te tayikofel wegdeg, hare mele sima luwallel chog kofach llufulyach, hare hasong; hachangcheng ila tema hattey yal ssong.  
\v 6 hachangcheng ila tema rraey irel wegdeg tayikof, bo yema rraey irel meka ye katos.  
\v 7 Hachangcheng ila yema yedamgel chog luwul tugulul ladep, mo luglug, mo malulu.   
\p
\v 8 Hachangcheng ila tema yug. Yor hapatpat kala yema hakkela depel yarmat. Iwe ngo ligdi bo be tor loh. Yor kkefang le hapatpat ka semat ye wel. Iwe ngo ligdi bo yebe tor loh. Yor repiy iwe ngo ligdi bo yebe tor loh.  
\v 9 Te pangal kkefang la be yoh le sibe medaf ngo ye yoh le sibe kapta mekla yalol Deus ngo yesa yoh ngalgich.  
\v 10 Bo yodla ye bela budoh mala ye hartael momay, ngo be chuyloh iye te yigil momay hemas.   
\p
\v 11 Yodwe ichil yalwich, ngo yai hapatpat mo lal depey mo yai luluwal, ila ye wochog yael semal yalwich, iwe ngo igla le isa mel bo semal mal, ila itay wegdegel yalwich.  
\v 12 Meka si wiri igla ila ye wochog yongel formel lal pipiy le te yigil ffod; bela yodla ngo sibele moch la kalfengal mo Deus. Lepal golayey igla ila yete palleng: ibele moch la gola pangal loh, le be lepal yael Deus golayey.   
\p
\v 13 Suluw formel le yebe mel chog: tugulul ladep, mo luglug, mo hachangcheng; ngo mala ye hartael palleng pelal mo luwul meka ila, hachangcheng.   
\c 14  
\s1 Wol Tot Kofael Kkefang Kala Espritu Santus Ma Fang  
\p
\v 1 Hachangcheng mele ye tugul le habe yedamgili. Ha itol chog dipmi irel kkefang kala Espritu Santus yema fang le pallengel ila kkefang la habe foloyu mala yalol Deus.  
\v 2 Yeramtala ma hapatpat irel semat hapatpat le ye wel, ila yete ma kapatpat ngal yarmat bo Deus mele yema kapatpat ngali, bo tor semal le be medaf irel. Yema tapeli mala kkelel Espritu Santus irel yal kapta mala ye katos la ye llebag.  
\v 3 Iwe ngo yeramtala yema foloyu mala yalol Deus, ila yema foloyu ngalir yarmat, ngo ye tipingir, ngo ye hakkela deper, ngo ye hafel lal deper.  
\v 4 Yeramtala yema hapatpat le tor le yema gola fal ila ye tipingi chog iy llufulyal, ngo yeramtala yema foloyu mekla yalol Deus ila yema tipingi pangal eklesia.   
\p
\v 5 Idipli le pangami ngo habe kapatpat le yarmat re towe gola fal. Iwe ngo ye kkel tot yai dipli bo yebe yoh ngalugmi kkefang la habe foloyu mala yalol Deus. Bo yeramtala yema foloyu mekla yalol Deus, ila ye palleng pelal mo imol yeramtala yema hapatpat le tor le ye gola fal. Iwe ngo hare yor semal le be hamdefa mekla ye kakapta, ila ngo be yoh le be tipingir panger yarmetael eklesia.  
\v 6 Yodla ibela buyoy iremi rewol bisiy, ngo meda pelay ngalugmi hare ibe yalol solbos le habe togla fal? Sugfed mwo ngo tor, igle ibe te kangalugmi mekla yalol Deus le sa kkewar ngalyey hare ifang repimi, hare ikangalugmi mekla Espritu Santus ye yetolong lal yai luluwal bo ibe kangalugmi, hare ikangalugmiy tot foloy.   
\p
\v 7 Mele ila ye wochog lital mosik kowe — le tappel \add flute\add* hare \add harp\add*— be ifa sengal ngo semal yesa gola digil le re kekakungu ngo teyiffod yalol?  
\v 8 Hare yeramtala ma hangung tawiy yete haffod yalol tawiy we, ila ngo itey le be hafelfel bela dabey fedeg?  
\v 9 Be ifa sengal ngo semal sa medaf irel mekla hama kapta kofal, le hare yete ffod yami kapta irel semat hapatpat le ye wel? Ila ngo mekla hama kapta ila be wochog molwe ha kaptaloh chog lal yayural.  
\v 10 Ye cholop yalol sew mo sew fuluy lal faileng le, ngo tor mele tor fal mo iyang.  
\v 11 Ngo hare ibe togla yalol fulula semal ye teptap, ila ngo ha bele gola le semal hamem ngo yarmetal sew fuluy.  
\v 12 Hare ye cchang dipmi be yoh ngalugmi kkefang la yael Espritu Santus, ila ngo habe yedamgili mekla yebe hatagita eklesia.   
\p
\v 13 Yeramtala ma hapatpat irel semat hapatpat le ye wel le si tugla fal, ila be ma mepel bo rebe ma fang kkelal bo be yoh le yebe hamdefa fael mekla yema kapta.  
\v 14 Hare ibe mepel le be iye sengal ngo ye katos le imepel. Ngo ligdi bo itemedaf irel mokwe ikapta.  
\v 15 Ila ngo meda mele ibe foru? Ibe ton ngo imepel irel semat hapatpat le tor le ye medaf iyang, ngo ibe wol ton ngo imepel irel semat hapatpat le yarmat rema medaf iyang.  
\v 16 Hare ha kangalu Deus yal hachigchig le ha teptap semat hapatpat le ye wel le tor le ye medaf iyang, ila ngo be ifa sengal ngo semal mo luwul chol ttey la sa sor bo, “Amen?” Towe yoh le yebe gola mekla ho sosor.  
\v 17 Ila mwo ye momay mepelel hachigchig la yam ngal Deus, ngo tor mele yebe tipingi ngal yeramtala semal.   
\p
\v 18 Ikangalu Deus yal hachigchig irel mala ila sallap mo imomi irel tot hapatpat le ye wel.  
\v 19 Be lal halesiya ngo idipli tot le ibe sor limpad hapatpat le yarmat rebe medaf iyang ngo re sala hamdefa ngalir sibis, mo imol mala ibe sor sangeras hapatpat le tor le ye gola fal.   
\p
\v 20 Hami rewol bisiy, ha towe dabey luluwal kowe yar yalwich. Habe far wochog yalwich le re ted gola mekla ye tayikof. Ha dabey luluwal kala yar cholellap.  
\v 21 Ye teftaf lal babior we ye santus le ye sor bo,  
\q1 “Samol ye sor bo, ibele kapatpat ngalir meka layi,  
\q2 le rechokwe rema teptap hapatpat kowe ye wel mele rebe hadayu ngalir,  
\q2 meka yaloy.  
\q1 Ibele hapatpat ngalir le chol sew fulu mo solbos mele rebe hadayu meka yaloy,  
\q2 iwe ngo ila mwo,  
\q2 ngo meka layi re towe talenga yaloy.”\x - \xo 14:21 \xt Is 28:11–12\x*   
\m
\v 22 Kkefang la ma yoh bo yarmat rebe teptap semat hapatpat le ye wel, ila hagillar rechokla re ted chepar — te rechokla resa chepar. Iwe ngo kkefang la ma yoh bo yarmat rebe foloyu mala yalol Deus, ila hagiler rechokla resa chepar — te rechokla re ted chepar.   
\p
\v 23 Hare hala ttey fengal pangami rechokla hasa chepar, ngo hasa teptap semat hapatpat le ye wel le tor le ye gola fal — ngo hare tot yarmat le re ted medaf hare sibis rechokla re ted chepar re sala budoh iremi, ila ngo re towe sor le pangami ngo hasa buch?  
\v 24 Ngo hare yodla panger yarmat ngo re kekapta mala yalol Deus ngo sala budoh semal rechokla re ted chepar, ila ngo yebe gola molfidil mo irel mokwe yesa rongrong. Bo mokwe yesa rongrong mele bele hatugulu kofal.  
\v 25 Mekla ye luluwaley le ye llebag ila bele llahloh. Bele hasrowu ngo ye mepel ngal Deus ngo bele sor bo, “Tosol mala Deus ila ye mel luwulumi!”   
\s1 Hafelfelel Mepel Lal Halesiya  
\p
\v 26 Hami rewol bisiy, iye mele ikekapta kofal. Yodla habe ttey fengal le habe mepel, ngo semal be yawli sew ton, ngo semal be foloy, ngo semal sa kapta mekla ye llah mo irel Deus, ngo semal be kapatpat irel semat hapatpat le ye wel. Iwe ngo yor semal le be hamdefa mala ye kekapta. Pangal meka ngo ye tugul le be tipingir yarmetael halesiya.  
\v 27 Hare habe teptap semat hapatpat la ye wel le tor le ye gola fal, ila ngo be halrumal hare solmol la rebe hapatpat, la be mol semal mo irel hapatpat, ngo semal sa moch hapatpat. Iwe ngo be mel semal la be hamdefa fael mokwe rechokwe re sosor.  
\v 28 Ngo hare tor semal mo loboswe le be hamdefa mokwe re sosor, ila ngo yeramtala be teptap hapatpat le ye wel, ila ye momay le towe hapatpat, bela kaptapat le be iy chog mo Deus.  
\v 29 Rumal hare solmol le sa yoh ngalir mala yalol Deus ila rebe kapta. Iwe ngo ikla sibis, ila rebe luluwaley fael mokwe rechokwe re kakapta.  
\v 30 Iwe ngo hare semal mo lal ttey we ye gola sew hapatpat mo irel Deus, ila ngo yeramtala ye kaptapat ila ye momay le yebe ppoloh.  
\v 31 Pangami ngo be yoh le habe kapta mala yalol Deus, le be semal mo semal hami, bo be pangal yarmat ngo rebe gola ngo ye kkel loh lal deper.  
\v 32 Kkefang le ye yoh ngal semal bo yebe kapta mala yalol Deus, ila ye momay le iy yeramtawe yebe kapta yebe hafel igegel yal tapeli kkefang la,  
\v 33 bo fael mala Deus yete dipli le sibe taroprop. Iy ye dipli le sibe mel le si pos.  
\p Irel pangal halesiya kala yael meka lol Deus,  
\v 34 ngo ye momay la fefel re towe ma maliliy, bo tetal le rebe maliliy lal ttey. Hatobtob we yar Jews ye sor bo, tor mele fefel rebe tamolu.  
\v 35 Hare rebe dipli bo rebe gola kofal sew formel, ila ngo resa kasiya mekla rir irel yodla re mel lubugter. Ye hamaama le semal fefel yebe hapatpat lal ttey la yar yarmetael halesiya.   
\p
\v 36 Hare ye budoh mala yalol Deus mo iremi? Hare hami chog mele ha rongrong?  
\v 37 Hare semal ye luluwaley bo iy yael Deus re hagloy, hare yor yal kkefang le Espritu Santus ye fang ngali, ila ngo ye tugul le yebe gola le meka iy tefa lal babior iy sa fangwey iremi ila yalol Samol.  
\v 38 Ngo hare yete itol depal irel mele ila ngo hami ha towe talenga yalol.   
\p
\v 39 Ila hami rewol bisiy, ha itol chog dipmi irel yami kapta mala yalol Deus, ngo ha towe happolahor yarmat mo irel yar teptap hapatpat la ye wel le tor le ye gola fal.  
\v 40 Ha faor pangal formel le be momay ngo ye fel igegal.   
\c 15  
\s1 Kristus Ye Molow Tefael Mo Irel Maes  
\p
\v 1 Hami rewol bisiy, idipli bo ibe hamangi ngalugmi Hapatpat Momay we ifoloyu ngalugmi we hasa talenga ngo sa tugul dipmi iyang.  
\v 2 Ila iy Hapatpat Momay we ifoloyu ngalugmi. Habe daor igle ha itol chog dipmi irel Hapatpat Momay le. Hare bete ila sengal ila ngo tor loh pelal tugulul ladep la yami.   
\p
\v 3 Isa kangalugmi meka ngang igula le ye hartael palleng fal: Kristus ye mes bo fael meka molfidich. Ila sengal le ye teftaf lal babior we ye santus.\x - \xo 15:3 \xt Is 53:5–12\x*  
\v 4 Re leba ngo solral mo wol miril ngo sa molow tefael mo irel maes. Ila sengal le ye teftaf lal Babior we ye Santus.\x - \xo 15:4 \xt Ps 16:8–10; Mt 12:40; Ac 2:24–32\x*  
\v 5 Ye moal llah ngal Pedrus, iwe ngo yesa moch llah ngalir panger apostel kowe seg mo rumal.\x - \xo 15:5 \xt Lk 24:34; Mt 28:16–17; Mk 16:14; Lk 24:36; Jn 20:19\x*  
\v 6 Iwe ngo sew chog yad ngo yesa llah ngalir mokwe re dabeyal we rebe ligdi limngeras. Dolper rechokla ila re chil molow ngo yor tot ir le resa rol mes.  
\v 7 Iwe ngo yesa llah ngal James. Iwe ngo la wol miril ngo yesa moch llah ngalir panger apostel kowe tot.   
\p
\v 8 Yela wol miril loh ngo yesa moch llah ngaliyey — le ila mwo iwochog semal le re dimolowagili le ye ted hola marmal.\x - \xo 15:8 \xt Ac 9:3–6\x*  
\v 9 Bo ngang mele ihartael totol mo luwullur panger apostel — tor igegay le rebe ffesangu ngalyey bo ngang semal apostel, bo fael mala ihafohoyur yarmetael eklesia la yael Deus.\x - \xo 15:9 \xt Ac 8:3\x*  
\v 10 Fael haradiya la yael Deus mele sa iye sengay iyang. Iwe ngo haradiya la ye fang ngalyey ila ye palleng pelal. Ye kkel yai yengang mo imor apostel kala sibis, ngo ligdi bo te ngang chog yai foru meka, bo haradiya la yael Deus ye tipingiyey.  
\v 11 Ila te tugul hare ngang mele ifoloyu hare ir, iwe ngo ika chog iy hapatpat kowe pangamem ngo hama foloyu. Ngo hami ha chepar iyang.   
\s1 Yach Molow Tefael Mo Irel Maes  
\p
\v 12 Hare hamem ha foloyu le Kristus ye molow tefael mo irel maes, ila ngo ifa sengal mala sibis hami re sor le chomes re towe molow tefael?  
\v 13 Hare ye katos mala ha sosor, ila ngo Kristus yete molow tefael mo irel maes;  
\v 14 iwe ngo hare te molow tefael Kristus mo irel maes, ila ngo tor mele hamem habe foloyu, ngo tor mele hami be tugul lal dipmi iyang.  
\v 15 Iwe ngo be wol llah le hamem ha kachepar kofal Deus, irel molwe hamem ha sor bo Deus ye hamolowa tefaeli Kristus mo irel maes. Bo hare ye katos le chomes re tema molow tefael mo irel maes, ila ngo Deus yete hamolowa tefaeli Kristus.  
\v 16 Bo hare chomes re tema molow tefael, ila ngo wol ila sengal Kristus bo te molow tefael mo irel maes.  
\v 17 Iwe ngo hare yete molow tefael Kristus mo irel maes, ila ngo tor pelael tugulul ladep la yami, ngo habe chil mel luwul mekla molfidmi.  
\v 18 Ngo wol sew mekla be budoh mo iyang, ila rechokla resa mes le luwul yar tugulul ladep irel Kristus ila re towe molow tefael.  
\v 19 Hare yach luglug ngal Kristus ila pelal ngal chog molow le si mel iyang igla, ngo tor pelal ngal ila sew, ila ngo gich mele yarmat be kkel yar fahogich mo lal faileng le.   
\p
\v 20 Iwe ngo ligdi bo mala katosal ila ye molow tefael Kristus mo irel maes. Ila mala tugulul le rechokla resa mes ila rebe wol molow tefael mo irel maes.  
\v 21 Bo maes ila hasiyeldoh semal mal; ngo wol ila sengal “molow tefael mo irel maes” bo hasiyeldoh semal mal.  
\v 22 Pangal yarmat ngo rema mes bo fael mala re sew chog mo Adam. Wol ila chog sengal yar pangal yarmat be molow tefael, bo fael mala resa sew chog mo Kristus.  
\v 23 Ngo ligdi bo semal ngo be molow tefael le be dabey mala ragregel le sa faesul tugul: Kristus mele metamol; iwe ngo yodla bela tefaldoh ngo resa moch molow tefael rechokla resa mel bo lol Deus.  
\v 24 Bela budoh miril faileng, ngo Kristus ye bele lamlirloh panger angelus kala re tayikof mo tamol mo rechokla yor kkeler, iwe ngo bele fang mala Lamliyal ngal Deus la Temal.  
\v 25 Bo Kristus yebe lamli pangal formel yee, yela hola yodla Deus be halusur ngo ye sururloh panger rechokla re hattohar ngali.\x - \xo 15:25 \xt Ps 110:1\x*  
\v 26 Mala hartal loh mo luwul pangal mekla ye hattohar ngal Samol, le Samol yebe hachuyaoh mala kkelel maes.  
\v 27 Bo babior we ye santus ye sor bo, “Deus yesa yitli pangal formel fael mekla pechel.” Ye ffod le mala re sor bo “pangal formel” ila ye tamel Deus iyang, le iy mele yesa itol Kristus bo yebe lamli pangal formel.\x - \xo 15:27 \xt Ps 8:6\x*  
\v 28 Yodla Deus ye bele foru le pangal formel ngo be mel bo lamliyel Kristus, ngo Deus bele lamli Kristus, bo yagel mala pangal formel ngo iy Deus mele yebe lamli.   
\p
\v 29 Ifa senger rechokla re baptismus bo yagilir rechokla resa mes — meda mele re luluwaley le be yoh ngalir? Hare ye katos mala sibis re sor le chomes re towe molow tefael mo irel maes, ila ngo meda fal le rebe baptismus bo yagilir rechokla resa mes?  
\v 30 Iwe ngo hamem — meda fal le habe mel chog luwul hammerah pangal yad iyang?  
\v 31 Hami rewol bisiy, pangal ral ngo ngang imel chog luwul weres. Yai cchehas iremi irel molow le yach le siya sew chog mo Kristus Jesus le yach Samol mele yela yoh le ikapta mele iyang.  
\v 32 Hare ye wochog bo ngang ima fedeg ngalir “mael ka re machoh” wol Ephesus le, lea idabey chog luluwal ka yach yarmat, ila ngo meda mmaley le ye budoh mo iyang? Iwe ngo hare chomes re towe molow tefael mo irel maes, ila ngo iye sengal molwe rema toa sor, “Siya rol mongoy ngo si rol yul bo walsu mele sibe mes.”\x - \xo 15:32 \xt Is 22:13\x*   
\p
\v 33 Ha hafalliy bo yarmat rede kacheprahmi. “Rechokla re tayikof ila rema hatayikofaloh wegdigir rechokla re momay.”  
\v 34 Ha tefael ngal luluwal kala yami le ye fel ngo hasa ligdi wegdeg tayikof kala yami. Mele ibe kapta ila habe maa iyang. Ye mel tot hami le ha togla Deus.   
\s1 Holong La Ye Molow Tefael Mo Irel Maes  
\p
\v 35 Yor sibis le rebe kasiy bo, “Be ifa sengal ngo chomes resa molow tefael mo irel maes? Be ifa sengal igegel mekla holonger?”  
\v 36 Hami ha rol buch! Yodla ha bela fadgu sefaes faesol ire ngo towe yoh le be tumul le be te mes.  
\v 37 Mala ha fadgu ila sefaes chog faesol ire, medalbo sefaes faesol \add wheat\add*, hare faesol semat \add grain\add* le ye towe tapel mala igegal irel yodla ye bela pallengdah iyang.  
\v 38 Deus mele ye foru igegel sefaes mo sefaes faesol ire irel yodla bela tumuldah, le ye faor ngal mala iy ye dipli. Iy mele ye fang ngal sefaes mo sefaes faesol ire mala holongol igegal irel yodla yebe tomuldah.   
\p
\v 39 Fodogol meka ye molow ila te pangal ngo ye hafedeg chog. Semat fodogol yarmat ngo semat fodogol mael, ngo semat fodogol mael yeyal, ngo semat fodogol yig.   
\p
\v 40 Yor mekla ye mel woal laeng ngo yor ikla ye mel woal talop. Momayel mekla ye mel woal laeng mo momayel ika ye mel woal talop ila yete hafedeg fengal;  
\v 41 Yaal ila semat loh chog momayel, ngo wol ila sengal meram bo semat momayel. Fiis ila semat momayel. Fiska chog ngo te hafedeg momayel.   
\p
\v 42 Be ila sengal igegar chomes irel yodla re bela molow tefael mo irel maes. Yodla ye liblib porog la ngo yebe mongongowloh. Iwe ngo bela molow tefael mo irel maes ngo tayor fael sew le be chil mes.  
\v 43 Yodla ye liblib ngo bele tayikof igegal ngo towol yor kkelal, ngo bela molow tefael mo irel maes ngo bele kamdidiy ngo ye kkel.  
\v 44 Yodla ye liblib ngo ye chil mel le holongol yarmat, ngo yodla bela molow tefael mo irel maes ngo tayor fael sew le yebe chil mes. Hare yor holongoch le yema mes, ila ngo be wol yor holongoch le tor fael sew le be mes.  
\v 45 Bo babior we ye santus ye sor bo, “Metamol yarmat ila Adam, le ye sub sala mel le ye molow”; ngo Adam la ye hamir ila yema fang molow.\x - \xo 15:45 \xt Gn 2:7\x*  
\v 46 Te yeramtala ye bidiy mo wol laeng mele yebe hamo, bo yeramtala ye budoh mo wol talop, iwe ngo sa moch ila ye bidiy mo wol laeng.  
\v 47 Mala metamol Adam ila ye budoh mo wol talop ngo ye budoh mo irel bol; ila harumalel Adam ila ye bidiy mo wol laeng.  
\v 48 Rechokla yarmetael talop ila re wochog yeramtala ye ffaor mo irel bol; rechokla yarmetal laeng ila re wochog yeramtala ye bidiy mo wol laeng.  
\v 49 Gich ila si wochog yeramtala ye ffaor mo irel bol, ngo si wol wochog Mal we ye bidiy mo woal laeng.   
\p
\v 50 Hami rewol bisiy, iye mele ikakapta kofael. Meka ye budoh mo irel fodog mo ccha, ila towe yoh le be hola mala Lamliyel Deus. Iwe ngo meka yema mes, ila towe yoh ngali le yebe wochog meka tema mes.   
\p
\v 51 Ha taelenga mele le yarmat re togla: te pangach ngo sibe mes, ngo ligdi bo yodla chog bela ddig mala hartael rappa ngo bele liwel meka holongoch,\x - \xo 15:51 \xt 15:51–52; 1 Th 4:15–17\x*  
\v 52 le be we fedal hamrup. Bo yodla bela ddig rappa la ngo chomes ila re bele molow tefael le tayor fael sew le rebe mes, iwe ngo pangach ngo bele liwel meka holongoch.  
\v 53 Bo mekla yema tayikofloh ila ye tugul le be liwel ngal mekla towe tayikof, ngo mekla be mes ila be liwel ngal mekla towe yoh le be mes.  
\v 54 Yodla bela weldoh mele, le sa liwel meka yema mes ngal ika tema mes, ila ngo bele ppalu ngal molwe babior we ye santus ye sor bo: “Deus sa hachuyaloh kkelel maes ngo iy mele sa kkel!”\x - \xo 15:54 \xt Is 25:8\x*  
\v 55 “Maes, ifa kkelem? Maes, ifa kkelem le hobe hafohoyur yarmat?”\x - \xo 15:55 \xt Ho 13:14 (LXX)\x*  
\v 56 Ye budoh kkelel maes mo irel molfid be hafohoyur yarmat. Iwe ngo ye budoh kkelel molfid mo irel Hatobtob we.  
\v 57 Iwe ngo sa hachigchig Deus le iy mele ye fang kkelach mo irel Samol la yach Jesus Kristus!   
\p
\v 58 Ila hami rewol bisiy le ihachangugmi, ha mel chog le yebe kkel dipmi. Ha itol chog dipmi irel yengang kala yael Samol bo hami ngo ha gola le te tor pelal yengang kala yal le hama foru.   
\c 16  
\s1 Maligach La Re Fang Bo Hammaler Rechokla Resa Chepar  
\p
\v 1 Ibele kapta kofael molwe ha teftafdoh babior irey we ha kasiydoh kofal: salpiy we habe hateyili bo hammaler mekla lol Deus wol Judea. Habe foru mekla isa kangalur yarmetael eklesia kala wol Galatia bo rebe foru.\x - \xo 16:1 \xt Ro 15:25–26\x*  
\v 2 Pangal Sunday ngo semal hami ngo ye hamuslaho sugfed salpiy la be fechfech ngal lepal salpiy la yema yoh ngali. Iwe ngo hasa haliliya salpiy le bo ila ngo iy bela budoh ngo tayor pelal le sibe wol hattey salpiy.  
\v 3 Yodla ibe buyoy ngo isa tefa sew babior bo hasiyer rechokla hami hasa duwler bo rebe hasiloh kkefang la yami wol Jerusalem le yebe hamdefa kofer.  
\v 4 Hare ye palleng fal le ngang ibe loh, ila ngo ir resa dabeyey hasa loh.   
\s1 Mekla Paulus Ye Luluwaley Be Foru  
\p
\v 5 Ibela tefael mwo mo wol Macedonia ngo isa moch buyoy iremi — bo towe mmal la ibe te loh wol Macedonia.\x - \xo 16:5 \xt Ac 19:21\x*  
\v 6 Medalbo be ssulay yai be mel iremi. Towe siy le ibe mel yee, yela chuy Llifang. Iwe ngo te tugul lobosle ibe loh iyang, ngo hami habe tipingiyey bo ibe taboloh yai malekah.  
\v 7 Idipli bo sibe rol werfengal le be ssulay yai mel iremi. Iyalyal hare be yoh le ibe ssulay ngalugmi igle ye fel mo irel Samol.   
\p
\v 8 Ibe mel wol Ephesus yee, yela hola mala Bungul Pentecost.\x - \xo 16:8 \xt Lv 23:15–21; Dt 16:9–11\x* \x - \xo 16:8 \xt 16:8–9; Ac 19:8–10\x*  
\v 9 Ila mwo ye cholop le yema hapaliyel ngalyey mo wol haplom le, ngo ye cholop yengang kala ye palleng pelal le be yoh le ibe foru.   
\p
\v 10 Hare ye buyoy Timothy iremi ngo hasa hakkula ngali bo yebe fel yal mel luwulumi. Bo iy ila yema foru yengang kala yael Samol le ye wochog ngang.\x - \xo 16:10 \xt 1 Co 4:17\x*  
\v 11 Tor semal le be tolpagili Timothy. Habe far tipingi bo yebe taboloh malekah la yal luwul hopos bo be yoh le be tefaldoh irey; ngang iwiwidi le bela tefael le be ir mo tot mekla wol bisich.   
\p
\v 12 Iwe ngo iye sengal mele kofael Apollos we bisich. Yesa cholop yai ma dding ngali bo yebe buyoy tefael mo iremi le be ir mo tot mekla wol bisich. Iwe ngo ted tugul hare be buyoy hare yeb. Sew yad le be mmal ngo sa moch buyoy iremi.   
\s1 Hartael Hapatpat  
\p
\v 13 Ha llugu dipmi ngo hasa mel chog le be kkel yami tugul, ngo hasa hakkela dipmi.  
\v 14 Pangal yengang kala yami ngo habe ma foru luwul hachangcheng.   
\p
\v 15 Hami ngo ha faesul gola molwe kofael Stephanas mo chol family we yal; ir mele metamol Kristiano le ye weg deper mo wol Achaia. Ngo ir chog yar fang ir bo lol Deus. Ikekefael pechehmi rewol bisiy,\x - \xo 16:15 \xt 1 Co 1:16\x*  
\v 16 bo habe talenga yalor ngo ha dabey wululur rechoka mo panger rechokla rema daber irel yengang.   
\p
\v 17 Yesa momay depey irel mele yesa budoh Stephanas, mo Fortunatus, mo Achaieus, resa mel irey irel yodle hami ha tamel iyang.  
\v 18 Resa harrayi lal depey le ye wochog yar harayugmi. Tappel rochoka ila habe ma itol dipmi irel meka rema sor.   
\p
\v 19 Yarmetael eklesia ka woal Asia re fangwey yar habong iremi. Aquila mo Priscilla, mo Kristiano kala rema ttey mo irel imwla imwer ila re fangwey yar habong iremi.\x - \xo 16:19 \xt Ac 18:2\x*  
\v 20 Panger meka wol bisich iga ngo re fangwey yar habong iremi.  
\p Habe ma fang fengal yami habong luwul yami ffaho fengal.   
\p
\v 21 Spegil ngang Paulus mele itefa mele: Habong ngalugmi mo irel Paulus.   
\p
\v 22 Semal le yebe te hachangi Samol ngo towe yolbuw!  
\p Marana tha — Yamem Samol, budoh!   
\p
\v 23 Haradiya la yael Samol Jesus be mel iremi.   
\p
\v 24 Hachangcheng le yai irel Kristus Jesus be mel iremi pangamiloh.   